detail_zh: 1 月 21 日搭高鐵來港，同日出現發燒及鼻塞，於西九龍站被發現發燒，即時送院。同行 4 名親人入住尖沙咀皇悅酒店， 1 月 22 日轉飛菲律賓馬尼拉。
detail_en: The patient travelled to Hong Kong via high-speed rail and developed fever and blocked nose on Jan 21, and was sent to the hospital immediately upon being detected with a fever at West Kowloon station. The other four family members stayed in Empire Hotel Kowloon-Tsim Sha Tsui, and then took a flight on Jan 22 to Manila, the Philippines.

detail_zh: 患者居於深水埗福華街華寶樓，無外遊記錄，12 月 15 日出現症狀。患者患有骨髓瘤，12 月 28 日曾到瑪嘉烈醫院內科日間病房接受治療，開始時有發燒，其後退燒。發燒於化療病人為常見現象，而患者當時沒有其他症狀。患者當日逗留約 5 小時 30 分鐘，其間曾除下口罩進食約 30 分鐘，同日完成療程後出院。其家人於早前確診，衞生防護中心通報瑪嘉烈醫院，再為患者進行檢測，其後確診。隨後瑪嘉烈醫院內科日間病房有其他病人及醫護相繼確診，而病人告於 1 月 22 日中午 12 時 42 分離世。
detail_en: The patient resides at Wah Po Mansion, Fuk Wa Street, Sham Shui Po, Kwai Chung, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on December 15. The patient has myeloma and visited the Medical Day Ward at Princess Margaret Hospital on December 28 for treatment, and experienced fever on-and-off, which is common when undergoing chemotherapy, and no other symptoms. The patient stayed from about 5 hours and 30 minutes, had a meal without mask for about 30 minutes, and was discharged on the same day. CHP informed the Hospital that her other family members diagnosed positive earlier on, and a test was arranged for the patient, returning a positive result. Other patients and medical staff members at the Medical Day Ward also diagnosed positive later on. The patient passed away at 12:42 p.m., January 22.

detail_en: The patient resides at Tat Sin House, Upper Wong Tai Sin Estate, Wong Tai Sin, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. Her specimen was passed on to CHP laboratory for re-examination by the hospital, returning a positive diagnosis on January 12 evening with a low viral load (CT value above 30).

detail_zh: 患者居於上水清河邨清頌樓，無外遊記錄，1 月 11 日出現症狀。患者於 1 月 14 日被送往雅麗氏何妙齡那打素醫院，同日轉送威爾斯親王醫院深切治療部接受隔離治療。病人經治療後，病毒抗體呈陽性，衞生署於 2 月 5 日解除其隔離令。病人其後繼續於深切治療部留醫，惟其病情持續惡化，延至 2 月 17 日晚上 6 時 42 分離世。

As the patient tests positive for the antibodies of the virus after treatment, his quarantine order was lifted by Department of Health on February 5. His conditions continued to deteriorate during his stay at the intensive care unit, and he passed away at 6:42 p.m., February 17.

His conditions continued to deteriorate, and he passed away at 3:58 a.m., April 9.

detail_en: The patient resides at Block 2, Uptown Plaza, Tai Po, has no recent travel history, and is a doctor at North District Hospital who was seconded from medical ward to intensive care unit. On January 15 he developed mild discomfort, and on January 17 he visited the accident & emergency department upon developing fever and diarrhea, returning a preliminary positive test result. He last attended work on January 17. His duties include taking care of patients diagnosed positive with the coronavirus. On January 5 he performed tracheal intubation at intensive care unit for a diagnosed patient (patient #9049) with personal protective equipment. While no other patients have been listed as close contacts of his, one of his family members with whom he lives together is a nurse at the medical ward of the same hospital. (A colleague at the same hospital, patient #9854, had also had contact with the same patient.)

detail_en: The patient resides at 18 Reclamation Street, Jordan, has no recent travel history, developed symptoms on January 13 and consulted a private doctor. At the time, he had developed symptoms however did not take a virus test. He later took a virus test on Dec 15 and Dec 18 at the community testing centre in Henry G. Leong Yau Ma Tei Community Centre and the mobile testing service on Canton Road. Both tests came out negative. The patient continued to feel unwell and was admitted to hospital on January 18. The hospital conducted a nasal swab and throat swab for testing, which came out positive and confirmed his diagnosis. His wife and son (patients #9811 and #9812) and two relatives (#9625 and #9642) have has been confirmed positive. (On February 9, CHP classified the patient's case as a local case.)

detail_zh: 患者居於元朗朗屏 8 號 5 座，無外遊記錄。患者為北區醫院內科護士，1 月 18 日出現輕微不適，19 日到社區檢測中心接受檢測，20 日獲通知初步結果為陽性。患者近 3 個月在隔離病房工作，日常臨床職務包括照顧確診病人，工作期間一直穿著合適個人防護裝備，最後上班日期為 1 月 14 日。患者於 1 月 5 日曾接觸過當時接受霧化程序的第 #9049 宗個案患者。( 同院工作的第 #9691 宗個案患者亦曾接觸同一名確診患者。)
detail_en: The patient resides at Tower 5, The Spectra, Yuen Long and has no recent travel history. The patient is a nurse at the internal ward at North District Hospital and developed mild discomfort on January 18. On January 19 she took a test at a community testing centre, and was informed on January 20 that the test returned a preliminary positive result. The patient has been working at isolation wards in the past three months, with clinical duties mainly in taking care of patients diagnosed with coronavirus and with full personal protective equipment. She last attended work on January 14, and she was in contact with patient #9049 on January 5 who underwent aerosol-generating procedures and also had contact with patient #9691 workign at the same hospital.

His conditions continued to deteriorate, and he passed away at 6:45 a.m., April 9.

detail_zh: 患者居於佐敦仁賢大廈，無外遊紀錄，1 月 22 日出現症狀。患者因發燒及需要氧氣支援，1 月 23 日由檢疫中心轉送北大嶼山醫院急症室接受治療，及後轉送瑪嘉烈醫院深切治療部留醫，並確診。 ​衞生署於 2 月 21 日解除其隔離令，惟患者情況持續惡化，延至 2 月 28 日晚上 9 時 49 分離世。
detail_en: The patient resides at Yen Yin Building, Yau Ma Tei, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on January 22. Due to fever and need for oxygen support, the patient was transferred from quarantine centre to the North Lantau Hospital emergency room for treatment on January 23. He was then transferred to the Intensive Care Unit at Princess Margaret Hospital for treatment and was diagnosed positive. On February 21, the CHP lifted the patient's quarantine order, however the patient's condition continued to deteriorated and he passed away on the evening of February 28 at 9:49pm.

detail_en: The patient resides at Block 3, Verbena Heights, Tseung Kwan O, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. On January 28, the CHP added in a press conference that the patient had passed away prior to diagnosis. The patient was a close contact of another earlier confirmed case. The patient had underlying health conditions and passed away due to her illness on January 15. Several days later, the family member she had lived with felt unwell and were subsequently diagnosed positive. The CHP contacted the Fu Shan Public Mortuary to take samples from the deceased patient and the test results came out positive.

detail_zh: 患者居於馬鞍山海栢花園 3 座，以及寶軒酒店（尖沙咀）。她為伊利沙伯醫院 A10 隔離病房護士，1 月 23 日早上下班後開始感到頭痛及喉嚨痛，1 月 24 日到伊利沙伯醫院急症室求診，測試後初步確診，獲安排入院接受隔離治療。最後上班日期為 1 月 23 日 ( 凌晨更 )，其日常的臨床護理工作包括護理確診病人，在工作期間有根據感染控制指引佩戴合適個人防護裝備，期間沒有進行高風險醫療程序。
detail_en: The patient resides at Tower 3, Bayshore Towers, Ma On Shan and The Bauhinia Hotel, Tsim Sha Tsui. She is a nurse at the isolation ward A10 at Queen Elizabeth Hospital, and developed headache and sore throat after duty on January 24 morning. She visited the accident & emergency department at Queen Elizabeth Hospital on January 24, tested preliminarily positive, and was hospitalised for isolation treatment. She last attended work on January 23 on an overnight shift. Her duties included caregiving for patients diagnosed with coronavirus with appropriate personal protective equipment, involving no high-risk clinical procedures.

detail_zh: 患者居於灣仔寶藝花園，為伊利沙伯醫院 E6 內科病房護士，1 月 22 日開始有咳嗽及喉嚨痛症狀，1 月 24 日到律敦治醫院急症室求診，測試後初步確診，獲安排入院接受隔離治療。患者曾於去年 12 月 7 日至本年 1 月 17 日期間在隔離病房工作，於隔離病房的臨床護理工作包括護理確診病人，在工作期間有根據感染控制指引佩戴合適個人防護裝備，期間沒有進行高風險醫療程序。曾於 1 月 13 日與第二名確診護士在工作上有短暫接觸，兩人均有佩戴合適個人防護裝備。患者在 1 月 18 日調回內科病房，最後上班日期為 1 月 22 日，於內科病房的臨床護理工作為一般護理工作，期間沒有進行高風險醫療程序，亦沒有接觸過確診病人。
detail_en: The patient resides at Po Ngai Garden, Wan Chai, and is a nurse at the medical ward E6 at Queen Elizabeth Hospital. He developed coughs and sore throat on January 22, and visited the accident & emergency department at Ruttonjee Hospital on January 24. Upon testing preliminarily positive, he was hospitalised for isolation treatment. The patient worked at isolation wards from December 7, 2020 to January 17, 2021, with duties including taking care of patients diagnosed with coronavirus with appropriate personal protective equipment, involving no high-risk medical procedures. He had brief contact with another diagnosed nurse on January 13 in a work setting, both with appropriate personal protective equipment. On January 18 the patient was transferred back to medical ward, and last attended work on January 22. His duties at medical ward include ordinary caregiving, involving no high-risk clinical procedures or contact with patients diagnosed with coronavirus.

On January 22 she developed runny nose, sore throat, and headache, and visited the accident & emergency department at Queen Elizabeth Hospital on January 24 about an hour into her work time. Upon testing preliminarily positive, she was hospitalised for isolation treatment. The patient last attended work on January 24, with duties including ordinary caregiving with  appropriate personal protective equipment, involving no high-risk clinical procedures or contact with patients diagnosed with coronavirus. As confirmed cases were reported at the building she resides at, the hospital did not rule out the possibility of community transmission.

detail_en: The patient has underlying health conditions, resides at Block A, Fuk Wo Mansion, Tai Kok Tsui, and has no recent travel history. On January 26, she was taken to the Emergency Room at Kwong Wah Hospital via ambulance due to shortness of breath. On the way to the hospital, she underwent cardiac arrest. Upon arrival to the hospital, medical staff performed cardiopulmonary resuscitation and intubation treatment and her heartbeat recovered. She was admitted to the Intensive Care Unit. On the afternoon of January 27, she tested preliminary positive. Her condition continued to deteriorate, and she passed away on the afternoon of the same day at 4:22pm.

detail_zh: 患者居於旺角上海街 647-651 號文華閣，無外遊記錄。患者為診所助護，於中環皇后大道中 122 號尚至醫療大樓 16 樓工作，主要工作為登記及量體溫。患者 1 月 25 日的檢測結果呈陰性，1 月 29 日午膳後發燒，體溫達 38 度，諮詢醫生同事意見後，該醫生認為僅屬普通感冒，而患者數日前才有陰性結果，故無安排她再做病毒檢測。患者工作至當日下班，之後再自行求醫，醫生同樣無要求她檢測。直到 2 月 1 日症狀持續，再做檢測，結果呈陽性。最後上班日期是 1 月 29 日，同日亦出現喉嚨痛症狀。
detail_en: The patient resides at Mandarin Court, 647-651 Shanghai Street, Mong Kok and has no recent travel history. She works as a clinic assistant at 16/F, Virtus Medical Tower, mainly responsible for registration and body temperature checking. She tested negative on January 25, and developed fever on January 29 after lunch, with body temperature reaching 38°C. Upon consulting a doctor who works there, she was not arranged for coronavirus test as it was deemed only normal flu, and she had a negative results just days before. The patient continued work for the rest of the day and visited a private practitioner, who did not arrange a test for her as well. Her symptoms persisted until February 1, and she tested positive for the virus. She last attended work on January 29 and developed sore throat on the same day.

detail_zh: 患者居於上水莆上村 15 巷，無外遊記錄，1 月 19 日出現症狀。 1 月 26 日因咳嗽及輕微咳血到石湖墟賽馬會診所求診，診所安排接受留深喉唾液樣本檢測，27 日新東聯網微生物科病毒化驗室通知樣本有滲漏需重新留樣本。1 月 28 日患者沒到診所拿樣本瓶，診所曾電話聯絡但沒人接聽。患者家人同日開始與患者失聯，1 月 29 日警方到患者居所破門入屋發現患者已離世。及後殮防在患者遺體採樣本檢測，2 月 3 日證實確診。患者曾於 1 月 16 日與一名非同住家人見面，該名家人於 1 月 21 日接受檢測，1 月 22 日確診。
detail_en: The patient resided at Lane No. 15, Po Sheung Tsuen, Sheung Shui, had no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on January 19. On January 26, he visited Shek Wu Hui Jockey Club General Outpatient Clinic upon developing coughs and a mild case of coughing up blood, where he was arranged to turn in a deep throat saliva sample for testing. On January 27, the microbiology laboratory of New Territories East Cluster informed that a resubmission of sample is needed due to leakage of the previous one, but the patient did not go to the clinic on January 28 or picked up the phone from the clinic, the same day the family of the patient lost contact with him as well. On January 29 the police broke into the patient's home and discovered that he already passed away. The mortuary obtained specimen from the patient's body which tested positive on February 3. On January 16, the patient met a family member who does not live with him, undertook test on January 21, and diagnosed positive on January 22.

detail_en: The patient has no travel history, turned in a specimen at Pok Oi Hospital, tested preliminarily positive on February 3, and went missing afterwards. On February 5, the CHP stated that the police had found the patient and had sent the patient to the community treatment facility at Asia World Expo. During the period he lost contact, he went to the Yuen Long Jockey Club Town Square and bought takeaways at Dragon Garden, Yuen Long. (On February 14, 2021, the CHP updated the patient’s onset date.)

detail_en: The patient resides in Shenzhen and arrived in Hong Kong from there on January 23 with an exemption from quarantine as a business traveller. detail_zh: 患者居於紅磡家維邨家廉樓，1 月 25 日起不適，2 月 5 日曾求醫，2 月 8 日早上在家中暈倒，11 時 15 分送往伊利沙伯醫院急症室，在負壓倉搶救室接受心肺復甦及插喉搶救後，同日中午 12 時 15 分不治，遺體被送往葵涌公眾殮房。其家傭（第 #10734 宗個案患者） 2 月 10 日凌晨 1 時左右因不適同樣到該院求診並檢測初步呈陽性，醫院遂聯絡葵涌公眾殮房，後在患者遺體驗出病毒，以及患者的血液對病毒抗體呈陽性。
detail_en: The patient resided at Ka Lim Lau, Ka Wai Chuen, Hung Hom, developed discomfort on January 25, and sought medical consultation on February 5. On February 8 morning he passed out at home and was admitted to accident & emergency department at Queen Elizabeth Hospital at 11:15 a.m. He was administered CPR and first aid at a negative pressure room, and certified dead at 12:15 p.m. on the same day, his corpse transferred to Kwai Chung Public Mortuary. His domestic worker (patient #10734) visited Queen Elizabeth Hospital around 1 a.m., February 10 upon developing discomfort and tested positive for the virus. Upon contact from the hospital, the mortuary performed test on the patient's body, which tested positive for the virus, and the blood testing positive for the antibodies of the virus.

detail_zh: 患者居於沙田禾輋邨富和樓，同時亦是該大廈的外判保安員，負責夜更保安工作，最近一次上班日期為 2 月 6 日晚上至 7 日早上，上班時一直有佩戴口罩，亦有接受體溫探測，體溫正常。她無外遊紀錄，屬早前富和樓確診個案的密切接觸者，2 月 7 日出現症狀，11 日被送往檢疫中心，翌日由檢疫中心送院。
detail_en: The patient resides at Foo Wo House, Wo Che Estate, Sha Tin and is also an outsourced security guard in the same building. She is responsible for the night shift and her last day at work was February 6 evening until February 7 morning. During her shifts, she wore her mask and would check her body temperature, which was regular. She has no recent travel history and is a close contact of a previously confirmed case in the building. She developed symptoms on February 7, was sent to the quarantine centre on February 11, and the next day was sent to the hospital from the quarantine centre.

detail_zh: 患者居於鑽石山嘉喜大廈，無外遊紀錄，在小童群益會賽馬會慈雲山青少年中學服務中心負責福利工作，平時有與親友聚餐，亦曾與中心義工或活動參加者進行小組討論及小組活動，每次約有十多人參與，期間有佩戴口罩。她在 2 月 7 日出現喉嚨痛症狀，最後上班日期為 2 月 9 日。其家人（第 #10775 宗個案患者）其後確診。
detail_en: The patient resides at Kellie Mansion, Diamond Hill and has no recent travel history. She works at the Boys & Girls Club Association Jockey Club Tsz Wan Shan C&Y ISC and is responsible for welfare work. She often has meals with relatives and friends, as well as group discussions and activities with the volunteers or activity participants in the centre. Each event has approximately ten or so participants, with everyone wearing masks during the event. She developed sore throat on February 7 and her last day at work was February 9. Her family member (patient #10775) later diagnosed positive as well.

He worked at Canal Street Market throughout February 6 to 8, mainly patrolling on his own and stationed at the security booth. On February 10 he worked at West Kowloon High Speed Rail Station, conducting patrol and inspection works.

detail_en: The patient resides at Lai Wo House, Tai Wo Estate, Tai Po, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 11.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者報稱無業，持有「行街紙」，居於尖沙咀華源大廈 C 座，早前因違反入境條例被捕，正等候遣返。她無外遊紀錄，2 月 9 日出現症狀，為第 #10735 宗個案患者的朋友，連同兩名初步確診的朋友早前曾互相探訪。
detail_en: The patient is reportedly unemployed, holds a Recognisance Form, and resides at Block C, Tsim Sha Tsui Mansion, Tsim Sha Tsui. She was arrested for immigration offences and is awaiting repatriation. She has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on February 9. She is a friend of patient #10735 and previously met with two friends who was diagnosed preliminarily positive.

detail_zh: 患者為機組人員，2 月 12 日由土耳其抵港，居於赤鱲角香港天際萬豪酒店，沒有病徵。衞生防護中心於 2 月15 日記者會補充患者檢測樣本的初步基因分析有 N501Y 變種病毒基因，需作詳細基因分析確認種類。
detail_en: The patient is a flight crew member arriving in Hong Kong from Turkey on February 12, was staying at Hong Kong SkyCity Marriott Hotel, Chek Lap Kok, and has exhibited no symptoms. At the February 15 press conference, CHP added that a preliminary genetic analysis of the patient's test sample reveals presence of the N501Y variant virus gene. Further genetic analysis is required to confirm the type.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為灣仔聖雅各福群會的社工，居於將軍澳新都城 1 期 1 座，無外遊紀錄，2 月 7 日出現發燒症狀。2 月 3 日曾與第 #10758 宗個案患者出席同一工作坊。
detail_en: The patient is a social worker at St. James' Settlement, Wan Chai, resides at Tower 1, Phase 1, Metro City, Tseung Kwan O, has no recent travel history, and developed fever on February 7. On February 3, he had attended a workshop with patient #10758.

detail_zh: 患者於香港電台任職髮型師，無外遊記錄，居於馬鞍山富寶花園 1 座，最後上班日為 2 月 11 日，同日出現上呼吸道症狀，2 月 12 日接受社區檢測呈陽性。患者於 2 月 9 日至 11 日有上班，其工作主要在化妝室為嘉賓及出鏡者整理髮型，其居住大廈為強制檢測大廈。
detail_en: The patient works as a hair stylist for RTHK, has no recent travel history, and resides at Block 1, Saddle Ridge Garden, Ma On Shan. He was last at work on February 11 and developed upper respiratory symptoms on the same day. On February 12, he tested positive at a community testing centre. He was at work between February 9 and 11 and primarily worked in the dressing room styling hair for guests and on-camera appearances. His residential buidling was a building designated for mandatory testing.

detail_zh: 患者無業，為印度籍尋求庇護者，居於土瓜灣土瓜灣道 267 號，無外遊記錄，2 月 12 日檢測呈陽性，沒有病徵。患者與友人同住，其居住大廈於 2 月 10 日因污水樣本呈陽而須強制檢測。
detail_en: The patient is unemployed and is an asylum seeker of Indian nationality. He resides at 267 To Kwa Wan Road, To Kwa Wan and has no recent travel history. He tested positive on February 12 and has exhibited no symptoms. He lives with a friend and the building he lives in was subject to mandatory testing on February 10 due to positive virus detection in sewage samples.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，1 月 31 日由印尼抵港，居於西營盤華麗都會酒店，抵港第 12 日樣本呈陽性反應，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic worker, arrived in Hong Kong from Indonesia on January 31, and was staying at Grand City Hotel, Sai Ying Pun. She tested positive on the 12th day after arrival and has exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於紅磡家維邨家廉樓，無外遊記錄，1 月 25 日出現症狀，其家人為早前確診個案，於病發及潛伏期均長時間留在家中。
detail_en: The patient resides at Ka Lim Lau, Ka Wai Chuen, Hung Hom, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on January 25. The patient's family member is a previously confirmed case. The patient stayed mostly at home during the onset date and incubation period.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於鑽石山嘉喜大廈，無外遊記錄，2 月 10 日出現症狀。患者為第 #10758 宗個案患者家人，在 2 月 12 日個案追蹤時已送往檢疫，當時已有病徵，其後確診。
detail_en: The patient resides at Kellie Mansion, DIamond Hill, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 10. She is a family member of patient #10758 and was already arranged for quarantine upon contact tracing on February 12, having developed symptoms and later diagnosed positive.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於尖沙咀美麗都大廈，去年由中國來港，與第 #10779 宗個案患者同住。患者無外遊記錄，2 月 12 日在衞生防護中心進行接觸者追蹤時已被安排入檢疫中心，2 月 13 日檢測呈陽性，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient resides at Mirador Mansion, Tsim Sha Tsui, arrived in Hong Kong from China last year, and resides with patient #10779. The patient has no recent travel history, was arranged for quarantine upon contact tracing by CHP on February 12, and tested positive on February 13, having exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於大埔廣褔邨廣智樓，與第 #10756 宗個案患者同住，無外遊記錄，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient resides at Kwong Chi House, Kwong Fuk Estate, Tai Po with patient #10756, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於尖沙咀美麗都大廈，去年由中國來港，近期無外遊記錄，2 月 8 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient resides at Mirador Mansion, Tsim Sha Tsui, arrived in Hong Kong from China last year, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 8.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於尖沙咀美麗都大廈，去年由中國來港，近期無外遊記錄，沒有病徵，與第 #10776 宗個案患者同住。
detail_en: The patient resides at Mirador Mansion, Tsim Sha Tsui, arrived in Hong Kong from China last year, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 8. She resides with patient #10776.

detail_zh: 患者居於葵涌打磚坪街寶星中心 A 座，無外遊記錄，在元朗任文職人員，2 月 11 日出現症狀，2 月 11 日在社區檢測中心檢測呈陽性。患者所居住大廈為強制檢測大廈。
detail_en: The patient resides at Block A, Po Sing Centre, Kwai Chung, has no recent travel history, works as a clerk in Yuen Long, and developed symptoms on February 11. She tested positive at a community testing centre on February 11, and the building she resides at has been ordered for compulsory testing.

detail_zh: 患者於屯門 V City Balencia 麵包店任職麵包師傅，居於天水圍天頌苑頌棋閣，無外遊紀錄，最後上班日期為 2 月 13 日，同日出現症狀，其後到天水圍醫院急症室求醫，確診後被轉送屯門醫院繼續治療。 患者 2 月 3 日曾接受公司安排的檢測， 結果為陰性。
detail_en: The patient works as a baker at V City Balencia bakery in Tuen Mun, resides at Chung Ki House Tin Chung Court, Tin Shui Wai, and has no recent travel history. The patient was last at work on February 13 and developed symptoms on the same day. He then went to the Accident & Emergency Department in Tin Shui Wai Hospital. After a positive diagnosis, he was transferred to Tuen Mun Hospital for further treatment. The patient had been tested as arranged by his company on February 3, but had a negative test result.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，由印尼抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic worker, arrived in Hong Kong from Indonesia, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，2 月 13 日由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。患者檢測樣本的初步基因分析有 N501Y 變種病毒基因，需作詳細基因分析確認種類。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic worker, arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines on February 13, and has exhibited no symptoms. A preliminary genetic analysis of the patient's test sample reveals presence of the N501Y variant virus gene. Further genetic analysis is required to confirm the type.

detail_zh: 患者為海員，由印度經杜拜抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a sailor, arrived in Hong Kong from India via Dubai, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 2 月 13 日由波蘭抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Poland on February 13 and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，由印尼抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic worker, arrived in Hong Kong from Indonesia, and has exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於荃灣龍華樓，無外遊記錄，沒有病徵，家人為早前確診個案，患者 2 月 14 日入住檢疫中心，其後檢測呈陽性。
detail_en: The patient resides at Lung Wah Building, 46-62 Chuen Lung St, Tsuen Wan, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. The patient's family member is a previously confirmed case. The patient was admitted to the quarantine centre on February 14 and later tested positive.

detail_zh: 患者於皇后大道中 59 至 65 號泛海大廈一律師行任職文員，居於杏花邨 26 座，無外遊記錄，2 月 9 日出現症狀。2 月 10 日求診，11 日交回樣本接受檢測，同日為最後上班日。患者於 2 月 12 日年初一曾到親友位於筲箕灣愛東邨愛平樓家中拜年。住在隔壁的 2 名鄰居（第 #10898 及 #10905 宗個案患者）其後確診，但兩家人並不相熟。
detail_en: The patient works as a clerk at a law firm in Asia Standard Tower, 59-65 Queen's Road Central, Central, resides at Heng Fa Chuen Block 26, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 9. On February 10, she sought medical consultation. On February 11, she returned her test sample for virus testing, which was also her last day at work. On February 12 (the first day of the lunar new year), she had visited relatives and friends at their home in Oi Tung Estate Block 2 Oi Ping House, Shau Kei Wan for new year greetings. Two next-door neighbours (patients #10898 and #10905) have also been confirmed positive, but the two households are not acquainted with each other.

detail_zh: 患者獨居於紅磡家維邨家廉樓，無外遊記錄，居住大廈早前因出現確診須強制檢測，患者在 2 月 13 日進行檢測後確診，沒有病徵。患者曾於 2 月 11 日到過牛頭角彩頤居 A 座探親但並非拜年。
detail_en: The patient resides on her own at Ka Lim Lau, Ka Wai Chuen, Hung Hom, has no recent travel, and was diagnosed positive on February 13 after compulsory test is ordered for the building upon confirmed cases, having exhibited no symptoms. The patient visited her relatives at Block A, Cheerful Court, Ngau Tai Kok on February 11 but not as part of Lunar New Year celebration.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，2 月 2 日乘搭 5J272 航班由菲律賓抵港，居於灣仔香港灣仔帝盛酒店，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper and stays at Dorsett Wanchai, Hong Kong, Wan Chai upon arrival in Hong Kong from the Philippines by flight 5J272 on February 2, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為家庭主婦，居於鑽石山鳳鑽苑，2 月 9 日出現發燒和頭痛症狀後一直留在家中，2 月 13 日到普通科門診求醫，翌日遞交樣本後初步確診。
detail_en: The patient is a housewife residing at Fung Chuen Court, Diamond Hill and has remained at home since developing fever and headache on February 9. On February 13 she visited a general out-patient clinic, turned in a specimen next day, and tested preliminarily positive.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，2 月 2 日乘搭 5J272 航班由菲律賓抵港，居於葵涌香港荃灣帝盛酒店，2 月 13 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper and stays at Dorsett Wanchai, Hong Kong, Wan Chai upon arrival in Hong Kong from the Philippines by flight 5J272 on February 2, and developed symptoms on February 13.

detail_zh: 患者居於元朗大生圍，為消防隊目，於葵涌消防局工作，最後上班日期為 2 月 10 日。他在 2 月 4 日開始出現頭痛、咳嗽和喉嚨痛症狀，曾自行服用成藥及感冒茶，2 月 14 日到博愛醫院求診；在傳染期期間，2  月 9 日曾到青衣及青衣南消防局替更，潛伏期則曾到訪元朗合益街市。
detail_en: The patient resides at Tai Sang Wai, Yuen Long and works as a Senior Fireman at Kwai Chung Fire Station, last attending work on February 10. He developed headache, coughs, and sore throat on February 4, and took medicine and cold relieving tea on his own. On February 14 he visited Pok Oi Hospital. During his infectious period, he took on relief duties at Tsing Yi and Tsing Yi South Fire Stations on February 9, and during his incubation period he visited Hop Yick Market, Yuen Long.

detail_zh: 患者為一名學生，居於石籬（二）邨石怡樓，隔鄰單位 3 人確診，但兩戶並不相熟。因所住大廈須強制檢測，她在 2 月 14 日到社區檢測中心接受檢測後初步確診，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a student residing at Shek Yi House, Shek Lei (II) Estate, Kwai Chung. Three people at her neighbouring flat diagnosed positive, but the two households are not acquainted. She undertook a test on February 14 at a community testing centre upon a compulsory testing order made for the building, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_en: The patient resides at Block A, Cheerful Court, Ngau Tau Kok, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 11.

detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者居於沙田乙明邨明恩樓，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient resides at Ming Yan Lau, Jat Min Chuen, Sha Tin, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者居於藍田匯景花園 1 座，無外遊紀錄，2 月 12 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient resides at Block 1, Sceneway Garden, Lam Tin, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 12.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者於荃灣都好燒臘粉麵飯茶餐廳任職廚師，居於深水埗福華大廈，無外遊紀錄，2 月 12 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient is a chef at a restaurant at 12 Hoi Pa St, Tsuen Wan, resides at Fuk Wa Mansion, Sham Shui Po, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 12.

detail_zh: 患者居於尖沙咀金冠大廈，無外遊紀錄，2 月 11 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient resides at Golden Crown Court, Tsim Sha Tsui, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 11.

detail_zh: 患者居於紅磡維港 ‧ 星岸 2 座，無外遊紀錄，2 月 14 日出現症狀。患者自去年 11 月後沒有工作，農曆新年期間有外出拜年，包括其親友位於元朗葡萄園的住處。
detail_en: The patient resides at Tower 2, Stars By The Harbour, Hung Hom, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 14. He has been out of work since November 2020. He had gone out to pay new year greetings during the Lunar New Year, including visiting relatives and friends at their residence in The Vineyard, Yuen Long.

detail_zh: 患者居於元朗康城大樓，無外遊紀錄，2 月 13 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient resides at Hong Shing Building, Yuen Long, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 13.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，2 月 15 日乘搭 CX906 由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵，由機場送院。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic worker, arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines on February 15 aboard flight CX906, has exhibited no symptoms, and was sent to hospital from the airport.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為消防員，居於油塘高翔苑高鳳閣，無外遊紀錄，2 月 11 日出現症狀，與第 #10793 宗個案患者於葵涌消防局工作。
detail_en: The patient is a fireman, resides at Ko Fung House, Ko Cheung Court, Yau Tong, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 11. He works with patient #10793 at Kwai Chung Fire Station.

detail_zh: 患者 2 月 15 日乘搭 QR818 由奧地利抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Austria on February 15 aboard flight QR818 and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者居於黃大仙安利大廈，無外遊紀錄，2 月 13 日出現症狀。患者於啟德道從事文職工作，最後上班日期為 2 月 10 日，農曆新年期間有外出拜年。
detail_en: The patient resides at On Lee Building, Wong Tai Sin, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 13. He is engaged in clerical work on Kai Tak Road and was last at work on February 10. During the Lunar New Year, he had gone out for new year's greetings.

detail_zh: 患者居於屯門富泰邨秀泰樓，為第 #10824 宗個案患者的家人，無外遊紀錄，1 月 15 日出現症狀。患者曾 3 次向中醫求診，平常多留在家中或到屯門時代廣場的好日子皇宴及煌府婚宴專門店飲茶，身體不適期間改到富泰商場的羊城海鮮火鍋酒家飲茶。2 月 15 日因身體嚴重不適而叫救護車送院，送院後發現其 CT 值為 41 ( 病毒量較低 )，而且已有抗體。
detail_en: The patient resides at Sau Tai House, Fu Tai Estate, Tuen Mun, is a family member of patient #10824, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on January 15. The patient had visited Chinese medicine practitioner three times and usually stayed at home or had 'yum cha' / dim sum at Haorizi Palace Banquet or Palace Wedding Banquet at Trend Plaza in Tuen Mun. During the time he was unwell, he switched to having 'yum cha' / dim sum at Province Hot-Pot and Seafood Restaurant in Fu Tai Shopping Centre, Tuen Mun. On February 15, due to serious physical discomfort, he called an ambulance and was sent to hospital. At the hospital, he was discovered to have a CT level of 41 (low viral load) and had already developed antibodies.

detail_zh: 患者居於佐敦高景臺，無外遊紀錄，2 月 14 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient resides at Highview, Jordan, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 14.

detail_zh: 患者 2 月 15 日乘搭 EK384 由巴基斯坦抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Pakistan by flight EK384 on Februray 15, having exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於元朗大生圍，無外遊紀錄，2 月 11 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient resides at Tai Sang Wai, Yuen Long, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 11.

detail_zh: 患者 2 月 13 日由巴基斯坦抵港，居於土瓜灣富薈馬頭圍酒店，2 月 15 日開始發燒，由酒店送院。患者檢測樣本的初步基因分析有 N501Y 變種病毒基因，需作詳細基因分析確認種類。
detail_en: The patient stays at iclub Ma Tau Wai Hotel, To Kwa Wan upon arrival in Hong Kong from Pakistan, and developed fever on February 15, thereafter hospitalised from the hotel. A preliminary genetic analysis of the patient's test sample reveals presence of the N501Y variant virus gene. Further genetic analysis is required to confirm the type.

detail_zh: 患者居於尖沙咀華源大廈 C 座，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient resides at Block C, Tsim Sha Tsui Mansion, Tsim Sha Tsui, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於鑽石山鳳鑽苑，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient resides at Fung Chuen Court, Diamond Hill, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，2 月 16 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on February 16.

detail_zh: 患者為家庭主婦，居於大埔 88 廣場，無外遊紀錄，2 月 11 日開始出現喉嚨痛和咳嗽症狀，2 月 16 日到雅麗氏何妙齡那打素醫院求醫，平日會光顧住所附近的餐廳。
detail_en: The patient is a housewife residing at 88 Square, Tai Po, has no recent travel history, and developed sore throat and coughs on February 11. On February 16 she sought consultation at Alice Ho Miu Ling Nethersole Hospital, and she usually dines at restaurants nearby her residence.

detail_zh: 患者有長期病患，於旺角帝京酒店餅店兼職，居於大圍雲疊花園 2 座，無外遊紀錄。2 月 15 日出現發燒症狀，17 日到私家診所求醫，19 日交樣本到醫管局普通科門診。由於症狀沒有減退，患者 22 日再向私家醫生求診，並轉送到威爾斯親王醫院，其後被安排入院。其鼻咽拭子檢測同日深夜驗出陽性，而早前提交的樣本亦呈陽性。其情況惡化，被轉往深切治療部繼續治療。帝京酒店表示患者曾於 2 月 16 日及 17 日於帝京餅店流動攤位上班，在18 日因未能提供陰性檢測報告而被拒上班。
detail_en: The patient has underlying health conditions, works part-time at Royal Plaza Hotel Cake Shop, Mong Kok, resides at Block 2, Carado Garden, Tai Wai, and has no recent travel history. She developed fever on February 15, consulted a private practitioner on February 17, and turned in a specimen on February 19. Seeing that the symptoms had not alleviated, the patient consulted a private practitioner again on February 22, and was transferred to Prince of Wales Hospital, later hospitalised. Her nasal swab sample tested positive at midnight on the same day, and the specimen she turned in earlier on also tested positive. Her conditions deteriorated and she was transferred to intensive care unit for treatment. Royal Plaza Hotel stated that the patient worked at a mobile kiosk at the Cake Shop on February 16 and 17, and was denied from work on February 18 upon unavailability of negative test report.

She last tested negative on February 22, and she visited the hospital for around 30 minutes with mask on. She had lunch at Mr. Ming's Chinese Dining, K11 Musea on February 18. On February 14, he had taken a virus test during off-work hours and tested negative. Between February 16th and 18th, he did not go to work. On February 18, he started coughing, and the next day he was at work until 4pm. As his onset date and dates at work are consistent with various factors, his case is temporarily considered the source of the cluster surrounding the K11 Musea restaurant Mr. Ming's Chinese Dining. (On March 14, 2021, the CHP classified the patient's case as a local one.)

She visited a private doctor for consultation on February 24 and submitted a deep throat saliva sample to a General Out-patient Clinic on the next day and later tested positive. The patient works as a financial secretary on the 13th floor of Kowloon Commerce Centre, Kwai Cheong Rd, Kwai Chung, and was last at work on February 23.

detail_en: The patient is a part-time faculty at The Hong Kong Academy of Performing Arts, resides at Seawide Mansion, Yau Ma Tei, has no recent travel history, and developed headache, coughs, and loss of sense of tasting on Feburary 23. On February 24 he tested positive at a community testing centre, and he did not attend work during incubation period.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者

A colleague working in the office room next door (patient #10917) tested positive earlier on. He tested negative for the virus on February 23, and retook the test on February 26 upon developing inflamed throat and muscle pain, later diagnosing positive.

On February 26 he visited a general out-patient clinic and diagnosed positive. The patient works as a security guard at the Central Kowloon Route – Kai Tak West Section construction site, and last attended work on Feburary 28.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者

detail_en: The patient resides at Mei Wui House, Shek Kip Mei Estate, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 27. Three of the patient's family members (patients #10938, $10966, and #10989) have also been diagnosed positive.

He last attended work on February 26.

Between February 25th and 26th, the patient stayed at the Marco Polo Hongkong Hotel in Tsim Sha Tsui for a staycation with patient #11043. On February 22, she visited the clinic of Dr Wong Chung Yan in Tai Kok Tsui. At the same time period, three members of the cluster surrounding Mr. Ming's Chinese Dining were at the clinic seeking consultation. At the time, she was right behind two of those members during payment.

detail_en: The patient resides at Sau Hong House, Sau Mau Ping Estate, Sau Mau Ping, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on February 23.

detail_zh: 患者居於清水灣香港科技大學高級教職員宿舍 7 座，無外遊紀錄，2 月 24 日出現咳嗽症狀。患者曾到科技大學一個辦公室工作，與同事開會，2 月 23 及 26 日曾到訪校內 LG4 健身室，2 月 21 及 28 日與朋友打網球，27 日於校園內的 University Bistro 用膳。其後兩名曾與患者一起工作及用膳的人士（第 #11055 及 #11056 宗個案患者）確診。一名曾與患者開會的內地返港 28 歲男子於 2 月 16 日在深圳進行病毒檢測呈陰性，翌日使用「回港易」乘坐私家車從深圳灣到港，在港居於坑口蔚藍灣畔 3 座，2 月 27 日乘搭 HX236 到達上海，其後在當地確診。該名男子本身有鼻敏感，在港時鼻敏感症狀加劇，來港前在深圳，在港期間曾到海港城購物。
detail_en: The patient resides at HKUST Senior Staff Housing House 7, has no recent travel history, and developed coughs on February 24. The patient previously worked at an office at HKUST and had meetings with his colleagues. He used the gym at HKUST LG4 on February 23 and 26, played tennis with friends on February 21 and 28, and dined at University Bistro on campus on February 27. Two persons who worked and dined with the patient (patients #11055 and #11056) later diagnosed positive. One of the attendees at a meeting attended by the patient returned to Hong Kong from Shenzhen by private car under the Return2hk scheme on Feburary 17, the day after he tested negative in Shenzhen. He resides at Block 3, Residence Oasis, Hang Hau. On February 27 he travelled to Shanghai by flight HX236 and was diagnosed positive there. He has nose allergy, the conditions of which aggravated during his time in Hong Kong, and he previously shopped at Harbour City.

She resides at Block 6, Kwai Shing West Estate, Kwai Chung, has no recent travel history, and last attended work on March 1, having exhibited no symptoms. She tested negative for the virus on February 13, and tested positive at a community testing centre on February 28.

He has no recent travel history and last attended work on February 24, developing coughs on the same day. He tested negative on February 13 when the building he resides at was ordered for compulsory testing. He tested positive for the virus on March 1.

On the same day she sought medical consultation at Evangel Hospital. Her test sample came out positive. She had recently been to Fook Yuen Seafood Restaurant in Kowloon City Plaza for yum cha / dim sum with her family.

detail_en: The patient is a housewife, resides at Mei Wui House, Shek Kip Mei Estate, Shek Kip Mei, has no recent travel history, and developed runny nose on February 28. Her test sample came out positive on March 1.

On March 4, the CHP added in a press conference that the patient is a faculty member at Sau Ming Primary School. On February 27, at 4pm, she had been to the cinema in K11 MUSEA to watch a movie. Her family member was an earlier diagnosed case.

Warehouse in Kowloon Bay. Her last day at work was March 2. On February 22, she developed cough and sore throat. On March 1, her test sample came out positive.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，居於荃灣愉景新城 1 座，在長沙灣政府合署 10 樓的小額薪酬索償仲裁處工作，日常不用接觸公眾，工作時亦有戴口罩，當值期間體溫檢測正常。他與家人曾於多間食肆用膳，2 月 27 日到荃灣冠荃美食中心、叁茶陸飯及沙田翠園；28 日到金鳳大餐廳和元氣壽司高速線；3 月 1 日到深水埗老地方茶餐廳、荃灣愉景新城潮食會和大家樂；3 日則獨自到深水埗潤發飯店。他於 3 月 1 日開始發燒，3 月 3 日最後一天上班，同日遞交樣本，其後確診。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history and resides at Tower 1, Discovery Park, Tsuen Wan. He works at the Minor Employment Claims Adjudication Board at Cheung Sha Wan Government Offices, has no contact with public, wears a mask during work, and tested normal body temperature when on duty. He and his family dined at numerous restaurants: Koon Tsuen (Tsuen Wan), Cha Fan (Tsuen Wan), and Jade Garden (Sha Tin) on February 27; Golden Phoenix Restaurant and Genki Sushi Train on February 28; 老地方茶餐廳 (Sham Shui Po), Yummy Corner (Discovery Park, Tsuen Wan), and Café de Coral (ditto) on March 1; and 潤發飯店 (Sham Shui Po) on his own on March 3. He developed fever on March 1, last attended work on March 3, and turned in a specimen on the same day, later diagnosing positive.

detail_zh: 患者為學生，2020 年 12 月起沒回校上課，居於秀茂坪曉麗苑曉暉閣。大廈早前須強制檢測，他與另一名患者居住於不同層數不同座向。2 月 22 日出現頭痛和發燒，3 月 1 日遞交樣本後確診。
detail_en: The patient is a student and has not attended classes in person since December 2020. He resides at Hiu Fai House, Hiu Lai Court, Sau Mau Ping which was earlier on ordered for compulsory testing. He and another patient resides on different levels and orientations. He developed headache and fever on February 22, and tested positive on March 1 upon turning in a specimen.

detail_zh: 患者居於石塘咀居仁閣，無外遊紀錄，在中環皇后大道中 100 號上班，最後一日上班為 2 月 26 日。3 月 1 日發燒，同日遞交樣本，其後確診，潛伏期內曾與同事一起吃飯。其 3 名家人（第 #11070、#11081 及 #11083宗個案患者）亦已確診。
detail_en: The patient resides at Kui Yan Court, Shek Tong Tsui, has no recent travel history, and works at 100 Queen's Road Central, last attending work on February 26. He developed fever on March 1, turned in a specimen on the same day, and tested positive. During incubation period he dined with his colleagues. Another three of his family members (patients #11070, #11081, and #11083) also diagnosed positive.

detail_zh: 患者為家務助理，居於油麻地金勳大廈的劏房，在清水灣小坑口一間村屋工作，最後上班日期為 2 月 23 日。2 月 28 日開始頭痛，3 月 2 日取樣本後確診。
detail_en: The patient resides at a subdivided flat at Honour House, 375-381 Nathan Road, Yau Ma Tei, and works as a domestic services assistant at a village house at Siu Hang Hau, Clear Water Bay, last attending work on February 23. She developed headache on February 28 and tested positive after turning in a specimen on March 2.

detail_zh: 患者由印尼抵港，居於北角華美達盛景酒店，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient stays at Ramada Hong Kong Harbour View, Sai Ying Pun upon arrival from Indonesia, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者由菲律賓抵港，居於何文田九龍維景酒店，沒有病徵。

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India by flight AI314 on March 4, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 3 月 4 日 由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines, having exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於石塘咀居仁閣，無外遊紀錄，3 月 4 日出現症狀。患者於紅鸞道祥祺中心 A 座 5 樓 502-503 室 OtterBox Hong Kong Limited 工作，最後上班日期為 3 月 3 日。其 3 名家人（第 #11064、#11081 及 #11083 宗個案患者），包括其外傭及就讀聖安多尼學校的女兒，亦已確診。
detail_en: The patient resides at Kui Yan Court, Shek Tong Tsui, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on March 4. THe patient works at OtterBox Hong Kong Limited, 502-503, Tower A, Cheung Kei Center, Hung Luen Road, last attending work on March 3. Another three of her family members (patients #11064, #11081, and #11083), including her daughter, a student at St. Anthony's School, and her foreign domestic helper, also diagnosed positive.

detail_zh: 患者居於灣仔克街 6 號廣生行大廈 B 座，無外遊紀錄，3 月 1 日出現症狀，3 月 3 日到政府門診求診，翌日交樣本呈陽性。患者於鰂魚涌英皇道太古坊林肯大廈一間電腦公司任職會計，最後一日上班是 2 月 17 日，其後在家工作。2 月 24 日曾到尖沙咀 K11 MUSEA 洗手間，逗留約 5 至 10 分鐘，2 月 24 日曾到尖沙咀安年大廈 15 樓參加物業投資講座，有戴口罩，當日有約 50 多名參與者，
detail_en: The patient resides at Block B, Kwong Sang Hong Building, 6 Heard Street, Wan Chai, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on March 1. He visited a government general out-patient clinic, and tested positive for the virus upon turning in a specimen next day. The patient works as an accountant at a computer company at Lincoln House, Taikoo Place, King's Road, Quarry Bay, last attending work on February 17 and thereafter working from home. On February 24 he went to a washroom at K11 MUSEA, Tsim Sha Tsui for about 5 to 10 minutes, and attended a property investment seminar, wearing a mask, at 15/F, Oriental Centre, Tsim Sha Tsui attended by another 50 people.

detail_zh: 患者已退休，居於將軍澳富寧花園第 1 座，無外遊紀錄，3 月 3 日出現症狀，同日由救護車送往急症室，傳染期曾光顧過多間食肆。
detail_en: The patient is a retired person residing at Block 1, Fu Ning Garden, Tseung Kwan O, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on March 3. He was hospitalised to accident & emergency department on the same day, and dined at several restaurants during infectious period.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為第 #11061宗個案患者家人，長沙灣政府合署勞工處一個部門工作，居於荃灣愉景新城第 1 座，無外遊紀錄，3 月 4 日出現症狀。兩名兒子 ( 第 #11078 及 #11079 宗個案 ) 及外傭 (第 #11080 宗個案患者 ) 均確診，兩名兒子分別就讀聖保羅男女中學中六及聖保羅書院中四。
detail_en: The patient is a family member of patient #11061 and works at a unit at Labour Department, Cheung Sha Wan Government Offices. She resides at Block 1, Discovery Park, Tsuen Wan, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on March 4. Her two sons, Form Six student at St. Paul's Co-educational College and Form Four student at St. Paul's College respectively (patient #11078 & #11079), and foreign domestic helper (patient #11080) tested positive for the virus.

detail_zh: 患者 3 月 2 日乘搭 TR980 由印尼抵港，同行者為早前確診個案，3 月 4 日出現症狀，於檢疫中心確診。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Indonesia by flight TR980 on March 2, and travelled with an earlier diagnosed patient. She developed symptoms on March 4 and diagnosed positive at quarantine centre.

detail_zh: 患者 2 月 28 日乘搭 EK384 由巴基斯坦經杜拜抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Pakistan via Dubai by flight EK384 on February 28, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 3 月 5 日乘搭 CX843 由美國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the USA by flight CX843 on March 5, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 3 月 5 日乘搭 CX843 由美國抵港，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the USA by flight CX843 on March 5, having exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於荃灣愉景新城 1 座，以及半山區聖保羅男女中學舍堂，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。患者為聖保羅男女中學中六學生，2 月 24 日為最後面授課程日期，患者居於宿舍至 3 月 4 日，與另一名同學同房，同層曾共用設施如沖涼房或洗手間、廚房，亦曾參與一些活動如打羽毛球。患者父母為早前確診個案 ( 第 #11061 及 #11073 宗個案患者 )、弟弟 ( 第 #11079 宗個案患者 )  及外傭 (第 #11080 宗個案患者 ) 亦於同日確診。
detail_en: The patient resides at Block 1, Discovery Park, Tsuen Wan and St. Paul's Co-educational College Residence Hall, Mid-Levels, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. The patient studies Form Six at St. Paul's Co-educational College, last attended face-to-face classes on February 24, and stayed at the residence hall until March 4, sharing the room with another classmate. Communal facilities used by residents on the same floor include showers, toilets, and kitchen, and the patient also took part in badminton playing among other activities. The patient's parents (patients #11061 and #11073) earlier diagnosed positive, and his younger brother (patient #11079) and foreign domestic helper (#11080) also diagnosed positive on the same day.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於荃灣愉景新城 1 座，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。患者為般咸道聖保羅書院中四學生，最後上課日期為 3 月 3 日。患者父母為早前確診個案 ( 第 #11061 及 #11073 宗個案患者 )、兄長 ( 第 #11078 宗個案患者 ) 及外傭 (第 #11080 宗個案患者 ) 亦於同日確診。
detail_en: The patient resides at Block 1, Discovery Park, Tsuen Wan, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. The patient is a Form Four student at St. Paul's College, last attending classes on March 3. The patient's parents (patients #11061 and #11073) earlier diagnosed positive, and his elder brother (patient #11078) and foreign domestic helper (#11080) also diagnosed positive on the same day.

detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper residing at Block 1, Discovery Park, Tsuen Wan, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. The family of the employer (patients #11061, #11073, #11078, and #11079) all diagnosed positive.

detail_en: The patient resides at Kui Yan Court, Sai Ying Pun, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. Another three of her family members (patients #11064, #11070, and #11081) also diagnosed positive.

detail_en: The patient resides at Hoi Sing Mansion, Taikoo Shing, Quarry Bay, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on March 1. He works in Kings Wing Plaza 2, Sha Tin, and has not been at the office since late February.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，3 月 5 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on March 5.

detail_zh: 患者居於深水埗大南街 258 號，無外遊紀錄，3 月 1 日出現症狀，3 月 5 日到檢測中心檢測，樣本呈陽性。患者於尖沙咀加拿芬道 2 號 4 樓 UNDONE LAB 任職電腦程式員，最後上班日期為 3 月 1 日。2 月 26 日曾到華嫂冰室，同日曾到 K11 MUSEA 4 樓看電影及使用該層洗手間。
detail_en: The patient resides at 258 Tai Nan Street, Sham Shui Po, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on March 1. On March 5, he went to a testing centre for testing and his sample later came out positive. He had worked as a computer programmer at UNDONE LAB on the fourth floor at 2 Carnarvon Road and his last day at work was March 1. On February 26, he had been to Wa So Cafe. On the same day, he went to the fourth floor of K11 MUSEA to watch a movie and also used the washroom on the same floor.

detail_zh: 患者已退休，居於葵涌海峰花園 1 座，無外遊紀錄，3 月 1 日出現症狀，曾求診中醫，3 月 5 日在社區檢測中心取樣後確診。
detail_en: The patient is retired, resides at Block 1, Regency Park, Kwai Chung, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on March 1. She had been to consult a traditional Chinese medicine practitioner. On March 5, she was diagnosed positive after sampling at a community testing centre.

detail_zh: 患者 2 月 15 日乘搭 CX829 由加拿大抵港，入住北角華美達盛景酒店，3  月 5 日出現喉嚨痛症狀，第 3 個檢測樣本呈陽性。其檢測樣本的初步基因分析有 N501Y 變種病毒基因，需作詳細基因分析確認種類。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Canada on February 15 aboard flight CX829, was staying at Ramada Hong Kong Grand View, North Point, and developed sore throat on March 5. The patient's third test sample came out positive. The preliminary genetic analysis of the test sample contained the N501Y variant virus gene, and further genetic analysis was required to confirm the type.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於馬頭圍君柏 1 座，無外遊紀錄，3 月 3 日出現症狀。

detail_zh: 患者居於馬鞍山錦英苑錦義閣，無外遊紀錄，3 月 5 日出現咳嗽症狀。患者於北角英皇道 430 號新都城大廈 B 座地舖佳坊任職地產經紀，最後上班期為 3 月 4 日，最近未有帶客人看樓盤，但於 3 月 2 日有業主曾到辦公室與患者對脹帳，3 月 1 日曾與家人到過明星金閣用膳。
detail_en: The patient resides at Kam Yee House, Kam Ying Court, Ma On Shan, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on March 5. The patient works as a real estate agent at Good Fit Property Agency, Metropole Building Block B, 430 King's Road, North Point and her last day at work was March 4. She had not brought any customers to visit apartments recently but had met with a property owner on March 2 in the office to settle some accounts. On March 1, she had had a meal with her family at Golden Star Seafood Restaurant.

detail_zh: 患者居於深水埗昌遠大廈，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient resides at Cheong Yuen Building, Sham Shui Po, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊記錄，3 月 7 日出現症狀，為第 #11040 宗人個案患者的家人。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, developed symptoms on March 7, and is a family member of patient #11040.

detail_zh: 患者 3 月 3 日由阿拉伯聯合酋長國抵港，入住何文田九龍維景酒店，3 月 6 日出現症狀。檢測樣本的初步基因分析有 N501Y 變種病毒基因，需作詳細基因分析確認種類。
detail_en: The patient stays at Metropark Hotel Kowloon upon arrival in Hong Kong from the UAE on March 3, and developed symptoms on March 6. The preliminary genetic analysis of the test sample contained the N501Y variant virus gene, and further genetic analysis was required to confirm the type.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，3 月 6 日由菲律賓抵港，沒有病徵。檢測樣本的初步基因分析有 N501Y 變種病毒基因，需作詳細基因分析確認種類。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper arriving in Hong Kong from the Philippines on March 6, having exhibited no symptoms. The preliminary genetic analysis of the test sample contained the N501Y variant virus gene, and further genetic analysis was required to confirm the type.

detail_zh: 患者居於元朗祥降圍，無外遊記錄， 3 月 6 日出現發燒症狀，同日到屯門醫院急症室求診，其後確診。患者於東涌映灣園 15 及 16 座任職保安員，最後上班日期為 3 月 6 日。
detail_en: The patient resides at Tseung Kong Wai, Yuen Long, has no recent travel history, and developed fever on March 6. He visited the accident & emergency department at Tuen Mun Hospital on the same day and diagnosed positive. The patient works as a security guard at Towers 15 and 16, Caribbean Coast, Tung Chung, last attending work on March 6.

detail_zh: 患者居於深水埗福榮街 15 號，無外遊記錄，3 月 4 日出現發冷症狀，3 月 5 日遞交樣本，其後確診。患者於尖沙咀星光行東翼 2 樓美心潮庭任職侍應，最後上班日期為 3 月 6 日。2 月 25 日曾接受檢測，結果為陰性。
detail_en: The patient resides at 15 Fuk Wing Street, Sham Shui Po, has no recent travel history, and developed chills on March 4. She turned in a specimen on March 5 and diagnosed positive. The patient works as a waitress at Chiuchow Garden Restaurant, 2/F East Wing, Star House, Tsim Sha Tsui, last attending work on March 6. She undertook a test on February 25, testing negative.

detail_zh: 患者為家庭主婦，居於尖沙咀彌敦道 83 至 97 號華源大廈賓館，無外遊記錄，3 月 4 日出現鼻塞症狀，3 月 5 日遞交樣本，其後確診。其同住家人早前不適，已到檢測中心留樣本，賓館其他分租人士須檢疫。
detail_en: The patient is a house wife, resides in a guesthouse at Tsim Sha Tsui Mansion, 83-97 Nathan Road, Tsim Sha Tsui, has no recent travel history, and developed blocked nose on March 4. She submitted her test sample on March 5 and was later diagnosed positive. A family member she resides with had felt unwell earlier and had already went to a testing centre to submit a sample. Other sub-tenants of the guesthouse will be quarantined.

detail_zh: 患者居於粉嶺綠悠軒 6 座，無外遊記錄，2 月 28 日出現咳嗽症狀，3 月 2 日遞交樣本，其後確診。患者為一名工程項目聯絡員，於觀塘順天邨天池樓辦公室上班，無需去地盤，最後上班日期為 3 月 6 日。

She had been with her family / friends to Tai O for hiking and a meal together. She had also accompanied a family member in a medical follow up consultation and admittance to hospital.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines, was staying at Ramada Hong Kong Harbour View, Sai Ying Pun, tested positive on the 12th day after arrival, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Bulgaria, was staying at Four Points By Sheraton Hong Kong, Tung Chung, Lantau Island, tested positive on the 12th day after arrival, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_en: The patient resides at Ibis Hong Kong Central & Sheung Wan Hotel, Sheung Wan as well as Pik On House, Yue On Court, Ap Lei Chau, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為旺角聖公會諸聖中學學生，無外遊紀錄，居於深水埗大南街 142-144 號，最後回校上課日期為 3 月 12 日，當日主要留在課室，全程有佩戴口罩，同日出現發燒及咳嗽症狀。3 月 16 日到流動採樣站接受檢測後確診。
detail_en: The patient is a student at S.K.H. All Saints' Middle School, has no recent travel history, and resides at 142-144 Tai Nan Street, Sham Shui Po. He last attended classes on March 12, mainly staying in the classroom with mask on, and developed fever and coughs on the same day. He tested positive at a mobile specimen collection station on March 16.

detail_zh: 患者居於堅尼地城士美菲路 85 號寶德大廈，為一名市場經理，在葵涌上班，最後上班日期為 3 月 15 日。她無外遊紀錄，3 月 6 日失去嗅覺，2 日後求診，未有按醫生建議檢測。3 月 16 日出現氣促，同日到社區檢測中心接受檢測後確診。
detail_en: The patient resides at Po Tak Mansion, 85 Smithfield, Kennedy Town, works as a market manager at Kwai Chung, and last attended work on March 15. She has no recent travel history, lost her sense of smelling on March 6, and although she visited a private practitioner two days later, she did not undertake a test as recommended by the doctor. On March 16 she developed shortness of breath, and tested positive at a community testing centre on the same day.

detail_zh: 患者居於荃灣綠楊新邨 F 座，為一名工程師，在長沙灣昌隆工業大廈工作，曾到長沙灣瓊林街及元朗山水盈的地盤，最後上班日期為 3 月 8 日。他無外遊紀錄，3 月 4 日出現喉嚨痛症狀，早前檢測結果不確定，3 月 6 日送院，醫院為他進行數次檢測仍是結果不確定。 3 月 10 日檢測呈陰性、有抗體，3 月 16 日遞交樣本後確診。
detail_en: The patient resides at Block F, Luk Yeung Sun Chuen, Tsuen Wan and works as an engineer at Cheung Lung Industrial Building, Cheung Sha Wan. He previously went to construction sites at King Lam Street, Cheung Sha Wan and Crescent Green, Yuen Long, last attending work on March 8. He has no recent travel history, developed sore throat on March 4, and had an inconclusive test result earlier on. He was hospitalised on March 6 and the several tests arranged by the hospital still returned inconclusive results. He tested negative for the virus but positive for the antibodies on March 10, and tested positive on March 16 upon turning in his specimen.

detail_zh: 患者居於鴨脷洲海怡半島美浚閣，無外遊記錄，3 月 17 日出現發燒症狀。患者於沙田新城市中央廣場 2 座 12 樓的亞爾康有限公司工作，最後上班日期為 3 月 16 日。其 4 名家人為早前確診個案（第 #10530、#10567、#10687 及 #10743 宗個案患者），均在 2 月發病 ，患者因此於 2 月 3 至 18 日於檢疫中心接受檢疫，於 2 月 4、8 及 15 日進行檢測，結果呈陰性。其 CT 值大於 30，病毒量較低。
detail_en: The patient resides at Mei Chun Court, South Horizons, Ap Lei Chau, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on March 17. He works on the 12th floor of Grand Central Plaza Tower 2 and his last day at work was March 16. Four of the patient's family members were previously diagnosed (patients #10530, #10567, #10687, and #10743) in February. Due to positive diagnoses of his family members, the patient was sent to the quarantine centre between February 3rd to 18th. On February 4th, 8th, and 15th, he underwent testing and his results came out negative. His CT levels are over 30 and the viral load is low.

detail_zh: 患者 3 月 17 日乘搭 PR300 由菲律賓抵港，於機場確診，沒有病徵。檢測樣本的初步基因分析有 N501Y 變種病毒基因，需作詳細基因分析確認種類。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines on March 17 aboard flight PR300, was diagnosed positive at the airport, and has exhibited no symptoms. The preliminary genetic analysis of the test sample contained the N501Y variant virus gene, and further genetic analysis was required to confirm the type.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Indonesia via Singapore on March 17 aboard flight SQ882 and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_en: The patient resides at Block B, Phase III, Kwan Yick Building, Sai Ying Pun, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on March 16. Two of the patient's family members (patients #11334 and #11356) have also been diagnosed positive.

The patient frequently has yum cha / dim sum at Chiu Fook Cuisine, Kai Tin Shopping Centre, last visiting on March 10 when we chatted with patient #11366 seated at the adjacent table. He often chats with the restaurant staff and neighbours at the restaurant.

detail_en: The patient stays at Metropark Hotel Kowloon, Hong Kong upon arrival in Hong Kong from Indonesia, and her specimen on the 12th day tested positive. She developed symptoms on March 17.

detail_zh: 患者居於將軍澳領凱第九座，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。患者於太古港島東中心 5 樓的里昂證券任職資訊科技從業員，每周 2 次到鰂魚涌多盛大廈 12 樓的 Joint Dynamics 健身室健身，最後一次到訪日期為 3 月 10 日。太古港島東中心之前於 25、26 樓及 61 樓曾有兩宗確診個案，為 URSUS Fitness 群組顧客。
detail_en: The patient resides at La Splendeur Tower 9, Tseung Kwan O, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. THe patient works at CLSA, 5/F, One Island East, Taikoo as a IT staff member, and works out at Joint Dynamics, 12/F, Dorset House, Quarry Bay, last visiting the gym on March 10. Two confirmed cases were earlier on reported on 25/F, 26/F, and 61/F at One Island East, who belong to the URSUS Fitness cluster.

detail_zh: 患者居於屯門翠寧花園第 6 座，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。患者於屯門麒麟圍村和生飯店任職廚房雜工，工作主要負責清潔雜務，毋須面對顧客或處理食物。3 月 15 日檢測結果為不確定，其後確診，其抗體呈陽性。
detail_en: The patient resides at Tsui Ning Garden, Tuen Mun, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. The patient works as a kitchen assistant at 和生飯店, Kei Lun Wai Village, Tuen Mun, mainly responsible for janitorial duties with no contact with customer or handling of food. His test result on March 15 was inconclusive, and he later diagnosed positive for the virus, testing positive for the antibodies.

detail_zh: 患者居於銅鑼灣加路連大樓，為一名負責木工的裝修工人，3 月 11 至 15 日曾到中環滙豐總行大廈 8 樓 及 11 樓做裝修，之後轉到士丹頓街地舖繼續工作，最後上班日期為 3 月 19 日。他無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵，因曾到訪滙豐總行而須強制檢測，3 月 18 日到流動採樣站接受檢測後確診。
detail_en: The patient resides at Caroline Hill Court, Causeway Bay and works as a woodworker. He carried out construction work at 8/F and 11/F, HSBC Main Building throughout March 11 to 15, and afterwards at the HSBC Staunton Street Branch, last attending work on March 19. He has no recent travel history, has exhibited no symptoms, was ordered for compulsory testing upon presence at HSBC Main Building, and diagnosed positive after testing at a mobile testing station on March 18.

detail_zh: 患者 2 月 15 日與家人乘搭 CX829 由加拿大抵港，2 月 16 日至 3 月 6 日在酒店檢疫，其間太太確診並帶英國變種病毒株病毒基因。患者其後於 3 月 6 日至 19 日在檢疫中心，一直沒有病徵，3 月 19 日檢測樣本呈陽性並帶有 N501Y 病毒基因，其 3 月 5 日及 8 日的樣本均為陰性，3 月 20 日樣本的病毒抗體呈陽性。患者沒出社區，一直留在酒店及檢疫中心。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Canada by flight CX829 with his family on February 15, and was under quarantine throughout February 16 to March 6 while his wife diagnosed positive with the UK variant of virus gene. The patient was then transferred to quarantine centre throughout March 6 to 19, having exhibited no symptoms. He tested positive on March 19 with N501Y variant virus gene, whereas he tested negative on March 5 and 8. He tested positive for the antibodies on March 20. Since arrival in Hong Kong the patient remained in hotel and quarantine centre with no contact with the community.

detail_en: The patient is a family member of patient #11367, resides at Wah Koon House, Wah Sum Estate, Fanling and Ping Yan House, Ping Tin Estate, Lam Tin, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on March 19.

detail_zh: 患者為巴基斯坦籍，報稱無業，持「行街紙」，5 至 6 個月前到港，3 月 19 日涉非法集結被警方拘捕帶返觀塘警署，因頭暈送院，檢測後呈陽性，當時 CT 值高（即病毒量低），有抗體，相信較早時間已確診。患者於 3 月 4 日及 18 日曾到青山灣入境事務中心簽文件。
detail_en: The patient is of Pakistani nationality, is reportedly not working, and holds a recognizance form ('going out pass'). He arrived in Hong Kong 5-6 months ago. On March 19 he was prosecuted by police with charges for illegal assembly, was hospitalised upon developing dizziness, and tested positive with a high CT value (denoting low viral load) and presence of antibodies, implying that he was diagnosed positive for the virus earlier on. The patient was present at Castle Peak Bay Immigration Centre on March 4 and 18 for signing documents.

detail_zh: 患者為貨機機師，隨 FX169 航班由美國經日本抵港，入住赤鱲角香港天際萬豪酒店，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient is a cargo pilot, arrived in Hong Kong from the US via Japan on flight FX169, was staying at Hong Kong Skycity Marriott Hotel, Chek Lap Kok, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines on March 18 aboard flight 5J273, was staying at Best Western Hotel Causeway Bay, Wan Chai, and was sent to hospital on March 19 after developing fever. The patient then tested positive. The preliminary genetic analysis of the test sample contained the N501Y variant virus gene, and further genetic analysis was required to confirm the type.

detail_zh: 患者 3 月 20 日乘搭 5J272 由菲律賓抵港，於機場確診，沒有病徵。

detail_zh: 患者 3 月 1 日乘搭 EK384 由巴基斯坦經阿聯酋杜拜抵港，入住葵涌香港荃灣帝盛酒店，抵港第 19 日檢測樣本呈陽性，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Pakistan via Dubai, UAE on March 1 aboard flight EK384, was staying at Dorsett Tsuen Wan, Hong Kong, Kwai Chung, tested positive on the 19th day after arrival in Hong Kong, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者任職替更日更市區的士司機（車牌 LE7673），居於小西灣邨瑞樂樓，無外遊記錄，3 月 15 日開始胃口欠佳。患者負責早班 ( 約早上 6 時至下午 3 時 )，於藍灣半島交更，曾於 3 月 3、10 及 17 日上班，平日主要在家中用膳。
detail_en: The patient works as an urban taxi driver (license LE7673), resides at Sui Lok House, Siu Sai Wan Estate, Chai Wan, has no recent travel history, and started having poor appetite on March 15. The patient is responsible for the early shift (around 6AM till 3PM), switches shifts at Island Resort in Siu Sai Wan, had been working on March 3rd, 10th, and 17th, and primarily has his meals at home.

detail_zh: 患者 3 月 9 日乘搭 5J272 由菲律賓抵港，入住尖沙咀華美達華麗酒店，抵港第 12 日檢測樣本呈陽性，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines on March 9 aboard flight 5J272, was staying at Ramada Hong Kong Grand, Tsim Sha Tsui, tested positive on the 12th day after arrival in Hong Kong, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines on March 9 aboard flight 5J272, was staying at Dorsett Tsuen Wan, Hong Kong, Kwai Chung, tested positive on the 12th day after arrival in Hong Kong, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines on March 9 aboard flight 5J272, was staying at Grand City Hotel, Sai Ying Pun, tested positive on the 12th day after arrival in Hong Kong, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者任職地盤文員，於茶果嶺道一土木工程拓展署海堤道維修保養合約工程地盤工作 ( 工程編號為 CV/2016/01)，居於牛池灣曉暉花園第 3 座，無外遊記錄，3 月 17 日開始喉龍不適，最後上班日期為 3 月 19 日，3 月 20 日接受檢測後確診。患者 3 月 6 日曾接受檢測，結果為陰性。3 月 14 日曾與家人到元朗開心花園農莊燒烤，3 月 19 日曾到油塘大本型 Grove Café，3 月 21 日到曾到彩雲商場的桃園制作粥麵餐廳，傳染期間曾與 1 至 2 名同事用膳。
detail_en: The patient works as a clerk at the construction site of CEDD Maintenance Contract for Seawalls and Navigation Channels (Contract No. CV/2016/01) at Cha Kwo Ling Road, and resides at Block 3, Scenic View, Ngau Chi Wan. She has no recent travel history, developed sore throat on March 17, last attended work on March 19, and tested positive on March 20. The patient previously tested negative on March 6. She went barbecuing at Happy Garden Farm, Yuen Long with her family on March 14, dined at Grove Café, Domain, Yau Tong on March 19, and MoMo Restaurant, Choi Wan Commercial Complex on March 21. During infectious period she had meals with one or two colleagues.

detail_zh: 患者為退休人士，無外遊記錄，居於藍田平田邨平善樓，3 月 17 日開始發燒。3 月 22 日凌晨因氣促及發燒經平安鐘服務轉介，由救護車送住基督教聯合醫院急症室求診，接受入院篩查測試，測試結果為初步陽性，隨即轉至隔離病房接受治療。患者家人表示 3 月 8 日至 14 日期間，患者每日早上到啟田商場潮福龍蝦專門店用膳。其居住大廈早前被例入強制檢測，患者居所與早前確診個案單位位於不同層數和座向。
detail_en: The patient is retired, has no recent travel history, resides at Ping Sin House, Ping Tin Estate, Lam Tin, and developed fever on March 17. In the early morning of March 22, the patient was admitted to the Accident and Emergency Department at United Christian Hospital due to shortness of breath and fever. The patient was referred by the Personal Emergency Link Service and was sent to the hospital by ambulance.  The patient went through an admission screening COVID-19 test and the result was preliminary positive. He was transferred to the isolation ward for further treatment. The patient's family member stated that between March 8th and 14th, the patient visited the restaurant Chiu Fook Cuisine (Shop 407) in Kai Tin Shopping Centre, Lam Tin every morning for meals. The patient's residential building was earlier subjected to mandatory testing. The patient's flat is on a different floor and faces a different direction from the flat of a previously confirmed case in the same building.

detail_zh: 患者為駐守西九龍總區刑事部的警員，於九龍城警務處西九龍總區總部 2 樓工作，居於藍田平田邨平仁樓，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。患者家人於 3 月 18 日確診，患者於同日接受檢測並獲安排接受隔離，其 3 月 20 日的檢測結果為不確定並驗出帶有抗體，3 月 22 日初步證實呈陽性反應。患者工作期間有佩戴口罩，並沒有與公眾接觸，最後上班日為 3 月 18 日。
detail_en: The patient is a police officer at the Criminal Division on the 2nd floor of the Kowloon West Regional Police Headquarters. He resides at Ping Yan House, Ping Tin Estate, Lam Tin, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. The patient's family member was diagnosed positive on March 18 and the patient underwent testing and was arranged to quarantine on the same day. On March 20, the patient's test result came out uncertain and showed signs of antibodies. On March 22, the result was confirmed to be preliminary positive. During work the patient had worn a mask and had not interacted with the public. His last day at work was March 18.

detail_en: The patient stays at Metropark Hotel Kowloon Hong Kong, Kowloon upon arrival in Hong Kong by flight EK384 on March 17, developed symptoms on the same day, and diagnosed positive during quarantine.

detail_en: The patient resides at Block 7, Fullview Garden, Siu Sai Wan, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on March 17. The patient works at Pao Yue-kong Library, The Hong Kong Polytechnic University, mainly working at the back office with little contact with library patrons.

detail_zh: 患者居於紅磡黃埔花園 3 期翠楊苑 6 座，無外遊記錄，3 月 17 日出現肌肉疼痛症狀。患者於葵涌和豐工業中心自設公司，平時與一名家人及一名司機一同工作，有時會上門組裝傢俬，最後上班日期為 3 月 23 日。其家人於 3 月 22 日幫患者交回檢測樣本，結果呈陽性。
detail_en: The patient resides at Block 6, Willow Mansions, Site 3, Whampoa Garden, Hung Hom, has no recent travel history, and developed muscle fatigue on March 17. The patient owns a business at Well Fung Industrial Centre, Kwai Chung, working with a family member and a driver, and sometimes provides door-to-door furniture assembly service, last attending work on March 23. His family member turns in a specimen of his on March 22, which tested positive.

detail_zh: 患者乘搭 EK384 由巴基斯坦經杜拜抵港，沒有病徵。檢測樣本的初步基因分析有 N501Y 變種病毒基因，需作詳細基因分析確認種類。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Pakistan via Dubai on flight EK384 and has exhibited no symptoms. The preliminary genetic analysis of the test sample contained the N501Y variant virus gene, and further genetic analysis was required to confirm the type.

detail_zh: 患者為日本籍空中服務員，去年 11 月後開始沒上班，沒有其他兼職。患者居於銅鑼灣禮頓道 62-64 號禮賢大廈，該單位有 9 至 10 個劏房，洗手間非共用。3 月 18 日出開始輕微喉嚨痛，20 日開始失去味覺，22 日因要去機場機鐵處理八達通事宜，順道在機場診所求診，醫生建議做測試，24 日到社區檢測中心採樣，結果呈陽性。3 月 11、12、17、18、19 及 23 日曾到北角和富中心 GO24 Fitness 健身中心上Pilates、瑜伽班及器械健身，其間有戴口罩。3 月 6 日曾到 Shake Shack，3 月 7 日曾到 DoubleShot Coffee，3月 15 日 及 24 日曾到上環 Pacific Coffee。患者 3 月 15 日於中山紀念公園體育館社區疫苗接種中心接種復必泰疫苗。
detail_en: The patient is a Japanese flight attendant who has not attended work since November last year and has no other part-time jobs. The patient resides at one of the nine to ten subdivided flats at Leigyinn Building, 62-64 Leighton Road, Causeway Bay, with no shared bathrooms. She developed mild sore throat on March 18 and loss of sense of tasting on March 20. On March 22 she went to Airport MTR station to handle matters of her Octopus card and visited a private practitioner at the clinic at airport, who recommended that she take a test. On March 24 she tested positive at a community testing centre. She went to GO24 Fitness for Pilates, yoga, and weight training on March 11, 12, 17, 18, 19, and 23, with masks on. She went to Shake Shack on March 6, DoubleShoot Coffee on March 7, Pacific Coffee in Sheung Wan on March 15 and 24. On March 15 the patient received at BioNTech vaccine shot at the community vaccine centre at Sun Yat Sen Memorial Park Sports Centre.

detail_zh: 患者為浸會大學學生，居於小西灣富景花園 7 座，無外遊記錄，3 月 25 日開始流鼻水，3 月 26 日接受強制檢測後確診。患者居住大廈早前因出現確診個案須強制檢測，其住所與第 #11419 宗個案患者的單位屬同一坐向、相隔4層。3 月 18 及 22 日曾回校上課，曾到過傳理視藝大樓、校園教學及行政大樓及善衡校園呂明才中心。3 月 21 日曾於維多利亞公園教小朋友踢足球。3 月 23 日曾與一名朋友在小西灣綜合大樓打羽毛球，3 月 25 日曾與家人到藍灣半島翠河餐廳用膳，3 月 26 日曾到鰂魚涌英皇道惠安苑上門為一名學生補習。
detail_en: The patient is a Hong Kong Baptist University student residing at Block 7, Fullview Garden, has no recent travel history, developed runny nose on March 25, and tested positive upon compulsory testing on March 26. The building the patient resides at was ordered for compulsory testing due to earlier confirmed cases, and his residence has the same bearing as that of patient #11419, with a difference of four storeys. The patient attended classes on March 18 and 22, having been present at Communication and Visual Arts Building, Academic and Administration Building, and Lui Ming Choi Centre, Ho Sin Hang Campus. He coached football for children at Victoria Park on March 21, played badminton with friends at Siu Sai Wan Complex on March 23, dined with family at Green River Restaurant, Siu Sai Wan Plaza on March 25, and tutored at a student's home at Westlands Gardens, King's Road, Quarry Bay on March 26.

detail_en: The patient works as a clerk at a property management company, resides at Block B, Phase 3, Kwan Yick Building, Sai Ying Pun, has no recent travel history, and developed runny nose on March 29. The patient was ordered for compulsory testing on March 17 upon confirmed cases identified at the building he resides at, and tested negative on March 18. His flat is located above that of the earlier confirmed patient. The patient works at 46-52 Portland Street, Mong Kok, and as part of work he patrolled company properties at 88 and 96 Nga Tsin Wai Road, 33 Cooke Street, at 2L Saigon Street, last attending work on March 29.  Two of the patient's family members (patients #11488 and #11489) have also been diagnosed positive.

He developed coughs and diarrhea on March 28, consulted a private practitioner on March 29, and turned in a specimen on the same day, later on diagnosing positive. The company of the patient is located at 1131-1133 Canton Road, Mong Kok, and he conducted work at Tower B, Manulife Financial Centre, Kwun Tong; Metro City Phase II; and Taikoo Place, among others, last attending work on March 27.

detail_zh: 患者居於炮台山五洲大廈，無外遊記錄，3 月 29 日出現氣促症狀，3 月 30 日到社區檢測中心接受檢測，其後確診。患者於灣仔金御海鮮酒家任職樓面，負責開茶，每周工作兩至三天，最後上班日期為 3 月 31 日，曾與其他同事吃午飯。患者有定期檢測，上一次檢測日期為 3 月 15 日，結果為陰性，其 3 月 30 日的檢測結果為初步陽性。
detail_en: The patient resides at Continental Mansion, Fortress Hill, has no recent travel history, and developed shortness in breaths on March 29. She undertook at test at community testing centre on March 30, later diagnosing positive. The patient works as a waitress at Majesty Chinese Restaurant, Wan Chai, responsible for setting the tea, and works around two to three days a week. She last attended work on March 31 and had lunch with other colleagues. The patient regularly undertakes the virus test, having tested negative on March 15, and preliminarily positive on March 30.

detail_en: The patient is unemployed, is a family member of patient #11502, resides at Tseung Kwan O Village, Tai Ngau Wu, Tseung Kwan O, and has no recent travel history. He developed symptoms on March 29 and visited an out-patient clinic on March 30. On March 17 he took part in a 7-on-7 football game at Sun Yat Sen Memorial Park Sports Centre without wearing a mask. On March 23 he went to NAMCO Gaming Center at PopCorn, Tseung Kwan O with his family on March 23. The patient also frequently buys takeaways at several restaurants at Metro City Phase II, including Café de Coral, Kam Kee Cafe, and Nam Kee Spring Roll Noodle, among others, which are mostly located on UG floor of Metro City Phase II. Patient #11476 carried out construction work at Super Super Congee & Noodle throughout March 19 to 25, which is located on the same floor as Kam Kee Cafe visited by this patient.

She visited the clinic of Dr. Tang Siu Tong again on April 7 due to persistent dizziness, who recommended that she undergo medical examination at a hospital. She previously dined and changed clothes with her colleages. On April 4 she and another 15 relatives and friends visited graves and dined at home. During work she dined at Tai Tong Road Cooked Food Market, Fu Do Restaurant, MOS Burger at KOLOUR‧Yuen Long, and McDonald's at Yuen Long Trade Centre. On March 25 she dined at Cafe 52's on G/F, The Rainbow, 22 Wang Yip South Street, Yuen Long with friends.

detail_en: The patient is the wife of patient #11617, and resides at Block 19, Meadowlands, Yuen Long with her husband and parents. She has no recent travel history and developed cough and sore throat on April 9. She took medicine by herself and felt better afterwards.On April 12, she began losing her sense of taste and smell, and visited Quality HealthCare Medical Centre, Lok Sing Building, Yuen Long for medical consultation. On April 13, she turned in a specimen for testing, and was diagnosed positive on April 14. The patient works as an accounting manager at Quality HealthCare Medical Services, Skyline Tower, 39 Wang Kwong Rd, Kowloon Bay, and is not involved in patient care or clinical services. Her last day at work was April 12 and she usually eats alone in the office. On March 30, she visited Mu Taiwan Noodles, Kwong Wah Street, Mong Kok with her husband and a law office at Regent Centre, Central. On April 2, she visited her friend's home at Hilltop Gardens, 33 Fung Shing St, Hammer Hill and ate at her friend's home. She dined with several relatives at her parents-in-law’s home at Sui Keung House, Siu Sai Wan Estate on April 3, 5, and 9. The aunt, uncle, and cousin (who all live at Block 11, Meadowlands) visited the patient's home on April 4 and 6. On April 4, she dined at aya, 26 Kin Tak Street, Yuen Long with her husband and her parents. She visited ALOT Living, Hau Ming Street, Kwun Tong on April 5. On April 9 she had been to the Don Don Donki at Island Resort Mall. On April 10, she visited Nail House at New Town Mall, Mong Kok for a manicure.

classification_zh: 輸入個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者在迪拜從事工程工作，3 月 19 日乘搭 EK384 由迪拜回港，3 月 19 日至 4 月 8 日期間入住尖沙嘴華美達華麗酒店接受 21 日檢疫，3 次檢測結果均為陰性，完成檢疫後，到佐敦白加士街的伯嘉士大廈的女友（第 #11672 宗個案患者）家暫住。4 月 9 日到過重慶大廈 A 座地下一間印度餐廳用膳，之後到過彌敦道金冠大廈渣打銀行及彌敦道 82-84 號匯豐銀行。4 月 14 日與朋友乘地鐵到中環，乘坐下午 3 時 15 分新渡輪往長洲，曾在長洲恒樂海鮮菜館用膳。原定 4 月 16 日返回迪拜，4 月 15 日到油麻地檢測中心做檢測發現陽性，並發現帶有 N501Y 變種病毒基因，其病毒值（CT Value）為 15 至 17，代表病毒量高。4 月 13 日曾與女友到女友母親（第 #11800 宗個案患者）家中聚會。
detail_en: The patient works in the field on construction in Dubai and arrived in Hong Kong from Dubai on March 19 aboard flight EK384. He was under a 3-week quarantine at Ramada Hong Kong Grand throughout March 19 and April 8, testing negative for the three times. After quarantine, he stayed at his friend's (patient #11672) home at Parkes Building, Parkes Street, Jordan. He dined at an Indian restaurant at Block A, Chungking Mansions, and went to the Golden Crown Court, Nathan Road Branch of Standard Chartered, and 82-84 Nathan Road Branch of HSBC. On April 14 he and his friends travelled to Central via MTR and took the 3:15 p.m. Sun Ferry to Cheung Chau, and dined at Hung Lok Seafood Restaurant there. He was set to return to Dubai on April 16, and tested positive at the testing centre at Yaumatei Community Centre on April 15. His test result was also found to contain the N501Y variant virus gene with a CT value of 15-17, denoting a high viral load. On April 13, he went with his friend to his friend's mother's (patient #11800) home for a gathering.

detail_zh: 患者居於牛頭角樂華北邨秉華樓，無外遊記錄，沒有病徵。患者任職器具維修工人，在九龍城承啟道工作，協助維修工程器具。於工作地點會與其他工友共用洗手間。曾到翠河茶餐廳、彌敦道倫敦大酒樓、觀塘廣場龍寶酒家及九龍城太子道西小曼谷海鮮燒烤屋用膳，4 月 10 日亦曾與 7 名朋友到過駿業熟食市場的 7 號檔聚餐。
detail_en: The patient resides at Ping Wah House, Lok Wah North Estate, Ngau Tau Kok, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. The patient is an appliance repair technician working at Shing Kai Road, Kowloon City, responsible for repairing consturction appliances. He uses a shared bathroom at his workplace with other construction workers, and previously dined at Green River Restaurant; London Restaurant, Nathan Road; 龍寶酒家, Kwun Tong; and Mini Bangkok Seafood and Grill, Prince Edward Road East, Kowloon City. He also had a meal gathering with seven other friends at Shop 7, Tsun Yip Cooked Food Market on April 10.

detail_zh: 患者居於屯門友愛邨愛暉樓第 2 座 8 樓，住在第 #11696 宗個案患者隔壁，無外遊記錄，4 月 15 日出現症狀。患者於元朗貿易中心香港人力資源有限公司任職電工導師，其教授的課堂較密集，一星期會上課 5 至 6 堂，每次兩個半小時，有約 30 名學生。患者多到安定商場大家樂及元朗福星樓嘩鬼拉麵用餐，該間大家樂早前亦有其他確診者到訪，友愛邨愛暉樓第三座早前有多宗確診。患者於 3 月 10 日及 4 月 7 日於屯門友愛體育館接種科興疫苗，7 天後，即 4 月 14 日採集的樣本對病毒病檢測呈陽性。
detail_en: The patient resides at 8/F, Block 2, Oi Fai House, Yau Oi Estate, Tuen Mun, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms April 15. The patient is an electrical engineering instructor at Hong Kong Human Resources Ltd., Yuen Long Trade Centre, teaching intensive courses with five to six 2.5-hour lessons per week to around 30 students. The patient usually dines at Café de Coral, H.A.N.D.S. and Ramen Noodle Limited, Fuk Sing Building, Yuen Long; the Café de Coral branch was previously visited by other diagnosed patients, and several cases were identified at Block 3, Oi Fai House, Yau Oi Estate. The patient was inoculated with Sinovac on March 10 and April 7, and tested positive for the virus seven days later (April 14).
