detail_en: The patient resides at Block 1, Scenery Court, Sha Tin, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為學生，未有接受面授課堂，與家人居於屯門泥圍菜園村村屋，無外遊記錄，4 月 11 日開始流鼻水，到私家醫生求診後進行檢測確診。患者在屯門市廣場 CHOCOOLATE 任職兼職售貨員，4 月 3 及 4 日有上班，平常會到屯門市廣場的麥當勞用膳。4 月 5 日去過曾咀靈灰安置所拜山，但與之前個案到訪時間不同。
detail_en: The patient is a student who has not been attending in-person classes yet, and  resides at Tsoi Yuen Tsuen, Nai Wai, Tuen Mun with her family. She has no recent travel history, developed runny nose on April 11. and tested positive upon visiting a private practitioner. The patient works as a part-time cashier at CHOCOOLATE, Tuen Mun Town Plaza, having reported duty on April 3 and 4. She usually dines at McDonald's at Tuen Mun Town Plaza. On April 5 she visited the graves at Tsang Tsui Columbarium, but at different time than that of previously diagnosed patients.

detail_zh: 患者居於屯門蝴蝶邨蝶翎樓，無外遊記錄，沒有病徵。患者於啟豐園商場川味閣任職廚師，有接受定期檢測，其 4 月 1 日的檢測呈陰性，至 4 月 14 日檢測呈陽性。4 月 6 日曾與 6 名親友去元朗烤魚工房用膳，4 月 9 日曾與 2 名朋友去過屯門鳳城皇宴聚餐，同日晚上與家人在蝴蝶邨的明星海鮮酒家用膳。
detail_en: The patient resides at Tip Ling House, Butterfly Estate, Tuen Mun, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. The patient works as a chef at Chuen Mei at Richland Shopping Arcade, Tuen Mun, and takes the virus test regularly. On April 1, she tested negative. On April 14, she tested positive. On April 6, she had been to How Fish Gong Fang in Yuen Long for a meal with 6 family and friends. On April 9, she had visited Fung Shing Restaurant with two friends and visited the Star Seafood and Roasted Goose Restaurant in Butterfly Plaza, Tuen Mun with family members that night for dinner.

detail_zh: 患者為紅色的士司機，居於友愛邨愛勇樓，無外遊記錄，4 月 12 日發燒後求診，檢測陽性。曾到友愛商場逛街，近乎每日會到友愛邨利群茶餐廳用膳。患者每日駕駛之的士車牌都不同：周一 PH8571、周二 KA8537、周三 VD5224、周四 LA8242、周五 8022。在 4 月 1、8 及 15 日均駕駛 LA8242。
detail_en: The patient is a driver of a red taxi, resides at Oi Yung House, Yau Oi Estate, Tuen Mun, has no recent travel history, developed fever on April 12, sought medical consultation and tested positive. He had recently been to H.A.N.D.S, Tuen Mun for shopping and visits Liqun Seafood in the mall for meals nearly every day. The license plate of the taxi the patient drivers is different per day: on Mondays PH8571, on Tuesdays KA8537, on Wednesdays VD5224、on Thursdays LA8242、on Fridays 8022. The patient drove LA8242 on April 1, 8, and 15.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，居於佐敦伯嘉士大廈，為第 #11643 宗個案患者的女友，為中央廣場 Optimal Family Health 診所職員，負責抽血及接待病人，最後上班日期為 4 月 15 日。男友 4 月 8 日完成檢疫後與患者暫住。她沒有病徵，在檢疫中心確診，發現同樣帶有 N501Y 變種病毒基因。4 月 13 日與男友到其母親（第 #11800 宗個案患者）家中聚會。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, resides at Parkes Building, Jordan, is the female friend of patient #11643. She works at Optimal Family Health, The Centrium, responsible for drawing blood and greeting patients and last attending work on April 15. After completing quarantine, her male friend stayed with her starting April 8. She has exhibited no symptoms and was diagnosed positive in the quarantine centre, when she also tested positive for the N501Y virus mutation. On April, she visited her mother's (patient #11800) home with her male friend.

detail_zh: 患者居於屯門友愛邨愛暉樓 2 座 8 樓，住在第 #11645 宗個案患者相鄰單位，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient resides at Block 2, Oi Fai House, Yau Oi Estate, Tuen Mun, in the unit adjacent to that of patient #11645, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 4 月 4 日乘搭 UK6395 由印度抵港，入住北角華美達盛景酒店，因家確診入住檢疫中心，沒有病徵。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India on April 4 aboard flight UK6395, was staying at Ramada Hong Kong Grand View, North Point, was admitted to the quarantine centre due to the positive diagnosis of a family member, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 4 月 6 日乘搭 5J272 由菲律賓抵港，入住北角華美達盛景酒店，抵港第 12 日樣本呈陽性，沒有病徵。檢測樣本的初步基因分析有 N501Y 變種病毒基因，需作詳細基因分析確認種類。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines on April 6 aboard flight 5J272, was staying at Ramada Hong Kong Grand View, North Point, tested positive on the 12th day after arrival, and has exhibited no symptoms. The preliminary genetic analysis of the test sample contained the N501Y variant virus gene, and further genetic analysis was required to confirm the type.

detail_zh: 患者 4 月 18 日乘搭 UK6397 由印度抵港，沒有病徵，家人亦為確診個案。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India on April 18 aboard flight UK6397 and has exhibited no symptoms. The patient's family member has also tested positive.

detail_zh: 患者居於荃灣麗城花園第二期第 4 座，無外遊記錄，4 月 16 日開始喉嚨痛，之後到私家醫生求診並留下深喉唾液樣本，其後確診。患者於在荃灣沙咀道達貿中心從事文職工作，最近上班日為 4 月 12 日。4 月 11 日與約 10 名家人及朋友去過尖沙嘴金馬倫道 33 號炉端金用膳，亦有到過美孚萬事達廣場的餃子妹上海雲吞麵及荃灣荃新天地商場的米線陣。
detail_en: The patient resides at Block 4, Phase 2, Belvedere Garden, Tsuen Wan, has no recent travel history, and developed sore throat on April 16. The patient visited a private doctor for medical consultation, left a deep throat saliva sample for testing, and was later diagnosed positive. The patient works in clerical work at International Trade Centre, 11 Sha Tsui Rd, Tsuen Wan, and her last day at work was April 12. On April 11, she visited Robata Kim, 33 Cameron Rd, Tsim Sha Tsui with 10 family members and friends for a meal. She also visited 餃子妹, Mount Sterling Mall, Mei Foo Sun Chuen and mixian sense, Citywalk, Tsuen Wan.

detail_zh: 患者 4 月 6 日由福建乘高鐵經深圳灣口岸約下午 5 時多抵港，其後在荃灣芙蓉大廈劏房單位家居隔離，抵港第 12 日樣本呈陽性，沒有病徵。患者與一名朋友同住，劏房其他單位有約 20 名住客，其同住朋友無業，曾到附近街市及 7-11 便利店。患者在中國分別於 2 月 19 日及 3 月 19 日接種兩劑疫苗，但疫苗牌子不詳。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Fujian via the Shenzhen Bay Port on high speed rail around 5pm on April 6 and quarantined at a sub-divided flat in Fu Yung Building, 1-5 Fu Yung Street, Tsuen Wan. She tested positive on the 12th day after arrival and has exhibited no symptoms. The patient resides with one friend who is unemployed and there are about 20 other people living in the other units of the sub-divided flat. She had been to the market and 7/11 convenience store nearby. The patient has received two doses of the vaccine prior to arrival on Feb 19 and March 19, however the brand of the vaccine is unknown.

detail_zh: 患者透過回港易在 4 月 6 日經深圳灣口岸由東莞約下午 2 時多抵港，抵港後居於荃灣青山公路新青大廈，來港前於在東莞居住 1 年，4 月 10 至 19 日期間曾到荃灣如心酒店做房務員，負責清潔執房，最後上班日期為 4 月 19 日。患者在曾與家人及一至兩名朋友到屯門三聖邨廣東名門海鮮酒家、荃灣嘉記燒味及佳記進食。患者於 4 月 7 日時檢測結果為陰性，惟抵港第 12 日樣本呈陽性。
detail_en: The patient returned to Hong Kong from Dongguan via the Shenzhen Bay Port on April 6 around 2pm through the Return2hk scheme. After arriving in Hong Kong, she stayed at Sin Ching Building, Tsuen Wan. She had been living in Dongguan for a year. On April 10th to 19th, she worked at Nina Hotel Tsuen Wan West as a housekeeper and her last day at work was April 19. She had recently been to the restaurants Chinese Legend at Tuen Mun, Ka Kee Roasted Meat Restaurant, Tsuen Wan and 佳記 in Tsuen Wan with her family member and one or two friends. On April 7, she tested negative. Her test on the 12th day after arrival was positive.

detail_zh: 患者居於大圍美田邨美庭樓，無外遊記錄，沒有病徵。患者任職地盤工人，在九龍塘聯福道 30 號地盤工作，該地盤為浸大學生宿舍及教學綜合樓項目的建築工地，與浸大校園不相通，工人亦不能進入校園範圍。患者有接受定期檢測，4 月 10 日結果為陰性，4 月 17 日檢測結果為陽性。患者曾到大圍龍順軒海鮮酒家、佐敦文記燒臘飯店、九龍塘聯合道百味閣餐廳、九龍塘金記冰室、又一城亞參雞飯、沙田大圍道燉奶佬、旺角雅蘭中心稻香漁港市集、大圍美林邨和大圍道麥當勞等。另曾到將軍澳厚德邨探望家人。
detail_en: The patient resides at Mei Ting House, Mei Tin Estate, Tai Wai, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. The patient is a construction worker at the site of 30 Renfrew Road, Kowloon Tong for a hostel and academic building complex project of Hong Kong Baptist University, which has no direct access to the university main campus; the construction workers do not have access right to the campus either. The patient undertakes virus tests regularly, having tested negative on April 10 and positive on April 17. The patient previously dined at Lung Shun Hin Seafood Restaurant, Tai Wai; Man Kee Roast Restaurant, Jordan; Lion Rock Bistro, Kowloon Tong; Kam Kee Cafe, Kowloon Tong; Asam Chicken Rice, Festival Walk; Daniel's Restaurant, Tai Wai Road; Tao Heung The Pier Market, Grand Plaza, Mong Kok; McDonald's at Mei Lam Estate and Tai Wai Road; etc. He also visited his family in Hau Tak Estate, Tseung Kwan O.

detail_zh: 患者為印尼籍外傭。3 月 20 日乘搭 SQ882 抵港，之後入住尖沙嘴華美達酒店，4 月 9 日完成隔離後返回油塘油麗邨雍麗樓的僱主住所。由於尖沙嘴華美達酒店被納入強制檢測，患者於 4 月 18 日接受強制檢測，其後確診，沒有病徵。患者完成隔離後曾到過鯉魚門街市以及藍田商場，4 月 11 日曾到藍田意八餐廳用膳。患者於酒店接受檢疫其間與第 #11550、#11544、#11643 及 #11672 宗個案患者同層。
detail_en: The patient is an Indonesian domestic helper, having stayed at Ramada Hong Kong Grand, Tsim Sha Tsui upon arrival in Hong Kong from Indonesia by flight SQ882 on March 20. She then resides at her employer's residence at Yung Lai House, Yau Lai Estate, Yau Tong upon completion of quarantine on April 9. As a compulsory testing order was made to Ramada Hong Kong Grand, the patient undertook a compulsory test and returned a positive result, having exhibited no symptoms. The patient visited Lei Yue Mun Market and Kai Tin Shopping Centre. She dined at ItaMoMo Cafe, Lam Tin on April 11. The patient stayed at the same floor as patients #11550, #11544, #11643, and #11672.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，4 月 8 日乘搭 5J272 由菲律賓抵港，入住油麻地香港海景絲麗酒店，沒有病徵。檢測樣本的初步基因分析有 N501Y 變種病毒基因，需作詳細基因分析確認種類。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic worker arriving in Hong Kong from the India, was staying at Silka Seaview Hotel, Yau Ma Tei, and has exhibited no symptoms. The preliminary genetic analysis of the test sample contained the N501Y variant virus gene, and further genetic analysis was required to confirm the type.

detail_zh: 患者 4 月 20 日乘搭 RA409 由尼泊爾抵港，沒有病徵，於機場確診。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal on April 20 aboard flight RA409, has exhibited no symptoms, and was diagnosed positive at the airport.

detail_zh: 患者居於屯門新圍苑新碧閣，為葵涌貨櫃碼頭理貨員，受僱宏記港務操作有限公司，在 1 號、2 號及 5 號碼頭工作，會使用 2 號碼頭寫字樓休息室，主要與 2 至 3 人共休。患者在碼頭外圍露天亭輪更工作，將來港貨櫃資料輸入電腦，不會接觸碼頭工友，毋須上船。4 月 17 日曾到屯門安定街市及屯門市廣場一幻拉麵，4 月 20 日到屯門良景廣場祥景茶餐廳。他無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵，因工作定期檢測而確診，病毒數值（CT Value）大於 30，即病毒量低，上一次 4 月 14 日檢測結果呈陰性。
detail_en: The patient resides at San Bik House, San Wai Court, Tuen Mun and works as a tally clerk at Kwai Tsing Container Terminals, employed by Wang Kee Port Operations Services Ltd. He works at Terminals 1, 2, and 5, and shares the rest station at Terminal 2 office with two to three other people. The patient works on rotation at the open area outside the terminals, responsible for inputting data of incoming freights; he has no contact with workers of the terminals and does not board any ship. On April 17 he went to H.A.N.D.S Market, Tuen Mun and dined at Ebisoba Ichigen, Tuen Mun Town Plaza. On April 20 he dined at Cheung King Restaurant, Leung King Plaza. He has no recent travel history, has exhibited no symptoms, and tested positive during regular testing for work. His CT value exceeds 30, denoting a low viral load, and he last tested negative on April 14.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India, was staying at Ramada Hong Kong Harbour View, Sai Ying Pun, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者 4 月 9 日乘搭 AI1314 由印度抵港，入住九龍城富豪東方酒店，4 月 19 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India on April 9 aboard flight AI314, was staying at Regal Oriental Hotel, Kowloon City, and developed symptoms on April 19.

detail_zh: 患者為日出康城的綠茵英文（國際）幼稚園主任，居於將軍澳新寶城 4 座，無外遊記錄，4 月 20 日開始發燒及咳嗽，同日到將軍澳頤康醫務中心求診，因發燒而被轉介到將軍澳醫院急症室。 患者有受接定期檢測，4 月 9日檢測結果為陰性，最後上班日期為 4 月 20 日，一般在接待處工作，4 月 20 日曾為兩班 K3 學生上課共半小時，為數 15 至 20 人。患者曾到朋友位於坑口邨的住所食飯，亦曾到天后 Camper’s 坐忘及銅鑼灣鮨幸用膳，以及到坑口的Physical健身。4 月 10 及 11 日曾到灣仔會展婚紗展、4 月 9 日到觀塘 Pole Beat Gallery 上瑜伽班、4 月 7 日到將軍澳中心 Bioscreen 美容。
detail_en: The patient works at Greenfield English International Kindergarten in Lohas Park, resides at Block 4, La Cite Noble, Tseung Kwan O, has no recent travel history. She developed fever and cough on April 20 and sought medical consultation from 頤康醫務中心 clinic in Tseung Kwan O on the same day. Due to fever, she was transferred to Accident & Emergency, Tseung Kwan O Hospital. The patient receives regular testing and tested negative on April 9. Her last day at work was April 20. She usually works at the reception desk. On April 20, she taught two classes of K3 students for a total of half an hour, comprising approximately 15 - 20 people. The patient had recently visited her friend's residence in Hang Hau Village to eat and had also visited Camper's in Tin Hau and Sushi Kou in Causeway Bay. She had also visited Physical Fitness in Hang Hau. On April 10 and 11, she visited the Wedding Expo at Hong Kong Convention and Exhibition Centre. On April 9, she visited Pole Beat Gallery in Kwun Tong for yoga class. On April 7, she had been to Bioscreen at Park Central, Tseung Kwan O.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Turkey on April 12 aboard flight QR818, was staying at Ramada Hong Kong Grand, Tsim Sha Tsui, and developed symptoms on April 15. detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines by flight 5J272 on April 13, developed runny nose on April 18, and was hospitalised from testing centre.

detail_zh: 患者居於鴨脷洲海怡半島怡麗閣，在葵涌 KC100 5 樓 YesStyle 工作，無外遊紀錄，4 月 21 日出現症狀。患者平常會去九龍貿易中心的 Pacific Coffee 用膳，4 月 18 日曾與家人去又一城商場，及到海怡半島的上海姥姥用膳，另亦曾到金鐘太古廣場的 Thai Basil 吃飯。
detail_en: The patient resides at Yee Lai Court, South Horizons, Ap Lei Chau and works at YesStyle, 5/F, KC100, Kwai Chung. She has no recent travel history and developed symptoms on April 21. The patient usually dines at Pacific Coffee at Kowloon Commerce Centre, and went to Festival Walk and Shanghai Lao Lao at South Horizons with her family on April 18. She also dined at Thai Basil at Pacific Place, Admiralty.

classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為西貢民政事務處司機，居住於將軍澳顯明苑，無外遊記錄，4 月 20 日出現症狀，最近上班日期為 4 月 21 日。4 月 16 日傍晚 7 時至 8 時曾到將軍澳舒適堡健身，與第 #11711 宗個案患者差不多時間出現。
detail_en: The patient is a driver of Sai Kung District Office residing at Hin Ming Court, Tseung Kwan O, has no recent travel history, and developed symptoms on April 20. He last attended work on April 21, and worked out at Physical Fitness, Tseung Kwan O on April 16 from 7 to 8 p.m., around the same time as patient #11711 did.

detail_zh: 患者為為外籍傭工，3 月 27 日從菲律賓抵港，入住西營盤華美達酒店 6 樓，完成隔離後，入住僱主於半山區堅尼地道 8 號 Kennedy Terrace 家中，4  月 22 日到社區檢測中心檢測後確診，沒有病徵。4 月 19 日曾到中環萬邦行做身體檢查，同日亦到過入境事務大樓 8 樓及皇后大道中 176 號錦安大廈的僱傭公司。檢測樣本的初步基因分析有 N501Y 變種病毒基因，需作詳細基因分析確認種類。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic worker, arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines on March 27, and stayed on the 6th floor of Ramada Hong Kong Harbour View, Sai Ying Pun. After quarantine, she moved into her employer's residence at Kennedy Terrace, 8 Kennedy Road, Mid-Levels. On April 22, she went to a community testing centre and tested positive. The patient has exhibited no symptoms. On April 19, the patient visited Melbourne Plaza, 6-16 Chiu Lung St, Central for a physical examination and on the same day also visited the 8th floor of the Immigration Tower and an employment agency at Kam On Building, 176 Queen's Road Central, Central. The preliminary genetic analysis of the test sample contained the N501Y variant virus gene, and further genetic analysis was required to confirm the type.

detail_en: The patient is a Filipina foreign domestic helper residing at Tower 11, Carmel Cove, Caribbean Coast, Tung Chung. She developed coughs on April 23 and visited a private practiioner three days later. On April 7 she tested positive at a community testing centre, carrying N501Y and E484K mutations from unknown sources. On April 18, she was at a gathering at 37 Fuk Wing Street, Sham Shui Po with patients #11793 and #11797. Three of the participants had earlier been at a separate gathering on April 13 at the home of patient #11800 in Hing Wah (II) Estate Fung Hing House, 18 Wan Tsui Rd, Chai Wan, where patients #11643 and #11672 were also in attendance.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，居於鰂魚涌康怡花園 N2 座，無外遊記錄，沒有病徵。與第 #11797 個案患者是朋友，二人曾共同外出及用膳。患者每周會到鰂魚涌街市買菜 2 次，4 月 25 日曾與朋友在中環一帶逛街，以及光顧干諾道麥當勞；5 月 1 日曾於天后一個鄰近維園的小公園休息；5 月 2 日朋友光顧西九龍中心的薩莉亞意式餐廳。4 月 18 日接種第一劑復必泰疫苗，驗出 N501Y 及 E484K 變種病毒株。4 月 18 日曾出席於深水埗福榮街 37 號與第 #11773 及 #11797 宗個案患者的聚會，聚會其中 3 名參加者早前曾出席 4 月 13 日於 第 #11800 宗個案患者於柴灣興華（二）邨豐興樓家中的聚會，第 #11643 及 #11672 宗個案患者當日亦有出席。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic worker, resides at Block N2, Kornhill, Quarry Bay, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. She is friends with patient #11797 and the two have gone out to dine together. The patient visits Quarry Bay Market and Cooked Food Centre twice a week to buy groceries. On April 25, the patient had gone shopping with friends in Central with friends and visited the McDonald's on Connaught Road. On May 1, she took a rest in a small park in Tin Hau next to Victoria Park. On May 2, she visited the Saizeriya restaurant at Dragon Centre in Sham Shui Po with her friend. The patient received her first dose of the BioNTech vaccine on April 18, and tested positive for the N501Y and E484K mutation. On April 18, she had been to a gathering at 37 Fuk Wing Street in Sham Shui Po with patients #11773 and #11797. Three of the participants in that gathering had earlier been to a gathering on April 13 at the home of patient #11800 in Hing Wah (II) Estate Fung Hing House, 18 Wan Tsui Rd, Chai Wan, where patients #11643 and #11672 were also present.

detail_zh: 患者 4 月 27 日乘搭 RA409 由尼泊爾抵港，入住油麻地香港海景絲麗酒店，5 月 2 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from Nepal on April 27 aboard flight RA409, was staying at Silka Seaview Hotel Hong Kong, Yau Ma Tei, and developed symptoms on May 2.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，居於薄扶林豪峰，無外遊記錄，沒有病徵。她平日多到堅尼地城的街市，曾與朋友（第 #11793 宗個案患者）到訪麥當勞及薩莉亞，5 月 3 日曾到堅尼地城的大快活，驗出帶有 N501Y 及 E484K 變種病毒株。4 月 18 日曾出席於深水埗福榮街 37 號與第 #11773 及 #11793 宗個案患者的聚會，聚會其中 3 名參加者早前曾出席 4 月 13 日於 第 #11800 宗個案患者於柴灣興華（二）邨豐興樓家中的聚會，第 #11643 及 #11672 宗個案患者當日亦有出席。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic worker, resides at Royalton, Pok Fu Lam, has no recent travel history, and has exhibited no symptoms. She usually visits the markets at Kennedy Town, and dined at McDonald's and Saizeriya with her friend (patient #11793). Her sample carries both the N501Y and E484K mutation. Ohe patient attended the gathering at 37 Fuk Wing Street on April 18 with patients #11773 and #11793, where three other patients previously attended the gather at the home of patient #11800 at Fung Hing House, Hing Wah (II) Estate on April 13, also attended by patients #11643 and #11672.

detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper staying at Ramada Hong Kong Grand, Tsim Sha Tsui upon arrival in Hong Kong from Surabaya, Indonesia by flight CX2780 on April 23, having exhibited no symptoms.

classification_zh: 輸入個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者為家庭主婦，第 #11672 號個案患者的母親，居於柴灣興華（二）邨豐興樓，5 月 5 日出現輕微發燒，送往東區醫院急症室，入院後採樣樣本呈陽性，有 N501Y及 E484K 變異病毒株基因。個案入院後 CT 值高，達 34，即病毒量低，抗體亦呈陽性。4 月 13 日曾與女兒及其男友（第 #11643 宗個案患者）於家中聚會。
detail_en: The patient is the mother of patient #11672, resides at Fung Hing House, Hing Wah (II) Estate, Chai Wan, and was admitted to Pamela Youde Nethersole Eastern Hospital on May 5 upon developing mild fever. The sample collected upon her admission tested positive and carried both N501Y and E484K mutations. Her high CT value denotes a low viral load, and she also tested positive for antibodies. On April 13 she had a gathering with her daughter and her daughter's boyfriend (#11643) at home.

detail_zh: 患者為機組人員，乘搭 RU5313 由俄羅斯抵港，沒有病徵。（衞生防護中心於 5 月 15 日記者會表示早前於 5 月 7 日確診的華大基因文職員工檢測仍然進行中，暫時未有陽性結果，政府和港大日前化驗為該男職員做基因測試分析源頭後，懷疑有機會是污染導致，此個案編號會重新編配給 5 月 16 日的確診患者。）
detail_en: The patient is a flight crew member arriving in Hong Kong by flight RU5313 from Russia, having exhibited no symptoms. (At the May 15 press conference, CHP stated that the test result for the BGI Health (HK) Company Limited clerical staff member diagnosed on May 7 is still pending, and no positive result is concluded. Testing conducted by the government and HKU suggested the possibility of cross-contamination. Therefore this case number has been re-assigned for a patient diagnosed on May 16.)

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，4 月 4 日乘搭 CX798 航班由印尼雅加達抵港，4 月 4 日至 4 月 24 日在油麻地海景絲麗酒店接受檢疫。患者在機場及隔離檢疫第 12 日及第 19 日樣本均呈陰性，完成檢疫後到僱主大埔林村放馬莆村住所。患者於 4 月 28 日強制檢測中呈陰性結果；5 月 5 日全港外傭強制檢測，結果呈陽性。而患者入院後再於醫院採樣，結果為不確定，抗體則呈陰性。患者並無病徵。
detail_en: the patient is a foreign domsetic helper arriving in Hong Kong from Jakarta, Indonesia by flight CX798 on April 4, and under quarantine at Silka Seaview, Hong Kong, Yau Ma Tei between April 4 and 24. The patient tested negative for the virus at the airport, and the 12th and 19th days since arrival, and began residence at her employer's home at Fong Ma Po, Lam Tsuen, Tai Po. The patient tested negative for the compulsory testing on April 28, and positive on May 5 under the compulsory testing order for foreign domestic helpers in Hong Kong. The patient's sample collected upon admission to hospital returned an uncertain result, and she tested negative for the antibodies, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, has exhibited no symptoms, and her CT value exceeds 30. The patient is the girlfriend of patient #11815 and works as a salesperson at URBAN Bakery, The Landmark, last attending work on May 4.

detail_zh: 患者 5 月 6 日前往法國，3 日後乘搭 QR818 返港，入住赤鱲角富豪機場酒店檢疫，5 月 11 日開始發燒。患者被驗出帶有 L452R 突變，是本港首宗由衞生署自行驗出的相關個案，不排除感染了印度變種病毒株 B.1.617。
detail_en: The patient travelled to France on May 6, returned to Hong Kong three days later by flight QR818, and was under quarantine at Regal Airport Hotel Hong Kong, Chek Lap Kwok. He developed fever on May 11 and the L452R mutation was detected in his sample, the first of its kind tested by Department of Health in Hong Kong; the possibility that it contain the B.1.617 variant from India has not been ruled out.

detail_en: The patient resides at Yee King Building, 67E Waterloo Road, Ho Man Tin and Block 13, Pak Tin Estate, Shek Kip Mei, and developed symptoms on May 12. He attends HKVNS Alumni Association Kindergarten (KCC) at 2 Liberty Avenue, Homantin. On May 13 he visited the clinic of Dr. Yeung Chiu Fat, Henry at Tsing Yi, turned in a sample bottle on the same afternoon, and diagnosed positive for the virus.

detail_zh: 患者 4 月 18 日乘搭 UK6397 由印度抵港，沒有病徵，帶有 L452R 變種病毒。
detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India on April 18 aboard flight UK6397, has exhibited no symptoms, and tested positive for the L452R mutation.

detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic worker, arrived in Hong Kong from India on May 7 aboard flight CX2780, was staying at Best Western Hotel Causeway Bay, Wan Chai, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為 4 個月大嬰兒，第 #11815 及 #11816 宗個案患者的兒子，無外遊紀錄，沒有病徵，帶有 N501Y 及 E484K 病毒。其祖母及姑媽（第 #11800 及 #11672 宗個案患者）亦已確診。
detail_en: The patient is a 4-month-old infant, the son of patients #11815 and #11816, has no recent travel history, has exhibited no symptoms, and tested positive for the N501Y and E484K mutations. The patient's grandmother and aunt (patients #11800 and #11672) have also tested positive.

detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic worker, arrived in Hong Kong from Indonesia on May 16 aboard flight CX798, was diagnosed positive at the airport, has a low viral load, and has exhibited no symptoms.

detail_en: The patient stays at Metropark Hotel Kowloon, Ho Man Tin upon arrival in Hong Kong from Indonesia, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，沒有病徵，4 月 25 日乘搭 GA876 由印尼抵港，抵港後在西營盤華麗都會酒店接受檢疫，其間曾在第 12 日及 19 日兩次檢測結果均為陰性； 5 月 16 日完成檢疫後，由僱傭中介帶她與其一名朋友到旺角 X 光醫學化驗所，其後再到將軍澳富康花園商場展欣服務有限公司辦手續，及後到深水埗南昌站上蓋住宅匯璽 5A 座的僱主家中。每日有帶狗外出散步一至兩次，其間沒有與其他人接觸。5 月 20 日到石硤尾白田檢測中心接受強制檢測時結果初步陽性，CT 值超過 30，病毒量低。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper, has exhibited no symptoms, and arrived in Hong Kong from Indonesia by flight GA876 on April 25. She was under quarantine at Grand City Hotel, Sai Ying Pun and tested negative on the 12th and 19th days since arrival. After completing quarantine on May 16, her employment agent took her and a friend to an x-ray and medical laboratory in Mong Kok; Hero Indonesia Limited, Beverly Garden Shopping Centre, Tseung Kwan O for processing; and the residence of her employer at Tower 5A, Cullinan West II, Cullinan West, Sham Shui Po. She walks the dog outside home once to twice a day, and has no contact with other people. On May 20, she tested preliminarily positive for the virus during a compulsory test at a community testing centre at Pak Tin Estate, Shek Kip Mei, with a CT value exceeding 30, denoting a low viral load.

detail_zh: 患者 5 月 19 日乘搭 CX881 由美國抵港，入住赤鱲角富豪機場酒店，5 月 21 日出現症狀。
detail_en: The patient stays at Regal Airport Hotel, Chek Lap Kok upon arrival in Hong Kong from The USA by flight CX881 on May 19, and developed symptoms on May 21.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，2 月 20 日乘搭 SQ882 由印尼經新加坡抵港，曾入住油麻地寶寧大廈 B 座的外傭中介臨時宿舍近 1 個月；4 月 6 日至 5 月 19 日到僱主在九龍塘伯爵園 B 座的家中居住。5 月 4 日檢測結果為陰性。由於她打算 5 月23 日離港返國，加上要再強制檢測，故 21 日到油麻地社區檢測中心再檢測，結果呈陽性，患者平常多在僱主家中，5 月 7 和 20 日曾到灣仔入境大樓 2 至 9 樓辦理手續。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic helper arriving in Hong Kong from Indonesia via Singapore by flight SQ882 on February 20, and stayed at a dormitory operated by an employment agency at Block B, Bell House, Yau Ma Tei for nearly a month. Throughout April 6 and May 19 she resided at the residence of her employer at Block B, Earl Gardens, Kowloon Tong. She tested negative on May 4, As she planned to return to Indonesia on May 23 and was under a mandatory testing order, she re-tested at a community testing centre in Yau Ma Tei on May 21, testing positive for the virus. The patient usually stays at the residence of her employer, and visited 2 to 9/F of Immigration Tower, Wan Chai on May 7 and 20.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭， 2 月 8 日與前僱主到巴基斯坦，4 月 3 日由巴基斯坦回港，入住西營盤華美達酒店檢疫，4 月 23 日完成檢疫。4 月 24 日到前僱主家人於青衣大王下村的村屋暫住，4 月 30 日搬到新僱主位於大角嘴維港灣 6 座的家中。患者 4 月 28 日的檢測樣本（ 抵港第 26 日 ）及 5 月 7 日外傭強制檢測樣本均呈陰性，5 月 22 日再度接受強制檢測呈初步陽性，其後確診並驗出 N501Y 變種病毒株，沒有病徵。患者於 4 月 28 及 5 月 19 日分別完成接種 2 劑 BioNTech 復必泰疫苗，4 月 26 日曾到觀塘新怡生工業大廈見外傭中介，5 月 9 和 16 日曾與朋友到中環海濱長廊休息， 5 月 16 日亦曾到中環環球商場匯款。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic worker, went to Pakistan with her previous employer on Feb 8, returned to Hong Kong from Pakistan on April 3, was staying at Ramada Hong Kong Harbour View, Sai Ying Pun, and completed her quarantine on April 23. On April 24, she stayed temporarily at her previous employer's home at Tai Wong Ha Tsuen, Tsing Yi then moved to her new employer's home on April 30 at Tower 6, Island Harbourview, 11 Hoi Fai Road, Tai Kok Tsui. Her test samples from April 28 (her 26th day since arriving in Hong Kong) and May 7 from the mandatory testing order for foreign domestic workers came out negative. However, on May 22, another test for a mandatory testing order came out positive. She tested positive for the N501Y mutation and has exhibited no symptoms. The patient completed both doses of the BioNTech vaccine on April 28 and May 19. On April 26, she went to a foreign domestic worker agency at East Sun Industrial Centre, 16 Shing Yip St, Kwun Tong. On May 9th and 16th, she had met with friends at the Central Section of the Central and Western District Promenade. On May 16, she had visited World-wide House in Central to remit money.

detail_zh: 患者為巴基斯坦籍男地盤工人，3 月 16 日由巴基斯坦返港，3 月 16 日至 4 月 5 日於荃灣香港遠東絲麗酒店酒店進行檢疫。檢疫完成後居於葵涌石籬（二）邨石華樓的住所。患者於將軍澳—藍田隧道—主隧道及相關工程的地盤工作（合約編號 NE/2015/01）。其 5 月 9 日的檢測結果為陰性，其後 5 月 23 日於荃灣蕙荃體育館社區檢測中心進行定期檢測並確診，沒有病徵。其 CT 值超過 30，顯示病毒量較低。
detail_en: The patient is a Pakistani male construction worker returning to Hong Kong from Pakistan On March 16, and was under quarantine throughout March 16 and April 5 at Silka Far East Hotel, Tsuen Wan, and thereafter returned to his residence at Shek Wah House, Shek Lei (II) Estate. The patient works at the construction site of the main tunnel of the Tseung Kwan O – Lam Tin Tunnel (Contract No. NE/2015/01), and tested negative on May 9. He later tested positive during a periodical test at the community testing centre of Wai Tsuen Sports Centre, Tsuen Wan, having exhibited no symptoms. His CT value exceeds 30, denoting a low viral load.

detail_zh: 患者為外傭，3 月 20 日由菲律賓抵港，3 月 20 日至 4 月 10 日期間於北角華美達盛景酒店進行檢疫。檢疫完成後在僱主位於西貢大洞禾寮村的住所居住。其 5 月 9 日的強制檢測結果為陰性，其後於 5 月 22 日到設於馬鞍山體育館的社區檢測中心進行檢測並確診，沒有病徵。患者樣本帶有 N501Y 變種病毒株及 E484K 變異基因，入院後對抗體測試呈陽性反應。患者 4 月 30 日及 5 月 11 日曾到入境事務處火炭辦事處，5 月 9 日及 16 日曾到訪其親戚位於馬鞍山海典居第 8 座的居所，亦曾於 5 月 1 日、2 日和 23 日到過馬鞍山公園。
detail_en: The patient is a foreign domestic worker, arrived in Hong Kong from the Philippines on March 20, and was in quarantine between March 20 and April 10 at Ramada Hong Kong Grand View. She then resides at the residence of her employer at Tai Tung Wo Liu Village, Sai Kong, and tested negative for the virus during a mandatory test. On May 22, she tested positive at a community testing centre at Ma On Shan Sports Centre, having exhibited no symptoms. The specimen of the patient contains both the N501Y and E484K mutations, and she tested positive for the antibodies upon admission to hospital. The patient visited the Immigration and Registration of Persons – Fo Tan Office on April 30 and May 11, visited the residence of her relative at Block 8, Villa Oceania, and went to the Ma On Shan Park on May 1, 2, and 23.

detail_en: The patient is unemployed, has exhibited no symptoms, and arrived in Hong Kong from Indonesia on May 18 with patient #11693 on flight UK6397. The patient underwent quarantine at Penny's Bay Quarantine Centre between April 18 and May 9. After completing quarantine, the patient lived at Shing Fu House, Kwai Shing East Estate, Kwai Chung. On May 13, the patient went to a community testing centre and received a negative test. On May 29, due to other illness, the patient was admitted to Princess Margaret Hospital.The test result was inconclusive, but the antibody test came out positive.

detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from the UAE, was staying at Metropark Hotel Kowloon, Ho Man Tin, and has exhibited no symptoms. (The CHP stated on June 2 that the 35-year-old police officer who was diagnosed previously on June 1 and who works at Wan Chai Police Station, carried a virus similar to the inactivated virus in the Sinovac vaccine. Thus it was suspected that this case involved contamination of the vaccine sample and this case was deleted. The case number will be allocated to a patient from June 2.)

detail_en: The patient, a close contact of patient #11873, stays at Ramada Hong Kong Harbour View, Sai Ying Pun upon arrival in Hong Kong from Austria via Doha by flight QR818 on May 31, having exhibited no symptoms.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，居於天水圍天盛苑盛譽閣，就讀於天水圍伊利沙伯中學舊生會湯國華中學，最後上學日為 6 月 2 日，同日出現喉嚨痛及咳嗽，翌日發燒，到天水圍門診求醫，同日留唾液樣本測試，其後確診。平日主要上學及留在家中，曾於 5 月 16、23 及 30 日到屯門德榮工業大廈 15 樓 306 室補習，5 月 29 日下午約 4 至 5 時與母親（第 #11859 宗個案患者）曾到灣仔會展 1C 展覽廳的香港國際教育展，其後在會展商場地下一間珠寶店 Deutsche Schenker-Gruppe HK 逗留，同日亦曾到旺角通菜街 187 號地下 Little Boss 寵物店購物，以及到通菜街敏華冰室用膳。患者 Ct 值偏低約 18，病毒量高，帶有 N501Y 變異病毒，為首宗本地源頭不明變種病毒個案。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, resides at Shing Yu House, Tin Shing Court, Tin Shui Wai, and studies at Queen Elizabeth School Old Students' Association (QESOSA) Tong Kwok Wah Secondary School, last attending classes on June 2, the day she developed sore throat and coughs. She developed fever next day and visited a clinic in Tin Shui Wai, turned in a saliva sample, and tested positive for the virus. She normally goes to school and stays at home, and attended tutorial classes at Room 306, 15/F, Tak Wing Industrial Building, Tuen Mun on May 16, 23, and 30. She and her mother (patient #11859) attended the Hong Kong International Education Expo at Hall 1C, Hong Kong Convention and Exhibition Centre, Wan Chai around 4 to 5 p.m., May 29. They also visited Deutsche Schenker-Gruppe HK at ground floor of the HKCEC Shopping Arcade afterwards, shopped at Little Boss, 187 Tung Choi Street, and dined at Men Wah Bing Teng, Tung Choi Street on the same day. The patient's CT value is 18, at a low level denoting a high viral load, and her specimen contains the N501Y, making her case the first of locally untraceable mutated virus.

detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，居於大埔運頭塘邨運亨樓，在香港國際機場擔任地勤，最後上班日期為 6 月 16 日，工作期間曾接待貨運航班的機組人員。患者亦有在大埔新達廣場任兼職，負責顧客服務，最後上班日期為 6 月 22 日。6 月 21 日出現發燒、喉嚨痛和咳嗽等病徵，同日在大埔運頭塘邨商場張毅醫生診所求診，翌日提交深喉唾液樣本，檢測結果呈初步陽性及顯示帶有 L452R 變種病毒。患者曾於 6 月 11 日在香港國際機場的衞生署臨時樣本採集中心與 3 宗印尼輸入個案（第 #11877、#11878 及 #11881 宗個案患者）有短暫相遇，基因排序亦顯示，患者的基因組與該 3 名患者基因組脗合。其同事（第 #11918 宗個案患者）其後確診。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, resides at Wan Hang House, Wan Tau Tong Estate, Tai Po, and works as a ground crew member at the Hong Kong International Airport, last attending work on June 16. His work entails contact with cargo flight crews. The patient also works part-time at customer service at Uptown Plaza, Tai Po, last attending work on June 22. On June 21 he developed fever, sore throat, and coughs, among other symptoms, and visited the clinic of Dr. Cheung Ngai on the same day. Next day, he turned in a deep throat saliva sample, testing preliminarily positive and containing the L452R mutation. The patient was in brief contact with three patients of imported cases from Indonesia (patients #11877, #11878, and #11881) at the Department of Health's temporary specimen collection station at the airport on June 11. He carried the genetic sequence identical to the genomes of the said three patients. His colleague (patient #11918) later diagnosed positive for the virus.

classification_zh: 輸入個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者居於香港仔利港中心，為油麻地紅茶館酒店的兼職清潔工，6 月 30 日在紅茶館酒店為多個房間清潔，包括早前確診的第 #11920 宗個案患者於 6 月 20至 27 日入住的 503 號房；她同日完成工作後到油麻地鴉打街流動採樣站檢測，結果呈初步陽性，CT值逾30（代表病毒量低），7 月 1 日確診，帶有 L452R 變種病毒。她另於鴨脷洲冠藍軒及淺水灣南灣道 12A 號 2 號兼職清潔，最後分別於 6 月 27 日及29 日上班； 6 月 26 日到香港仔大道海峰華軒陪同子女補習，6 月 27 日及 30 日與朋友到香港仔中心港富閣打麻將。衞生署稱患者入院後的病毒檢測和抗體檢測都是陰性，即無再驗到陽性，但體內亦無出現抗體，有無染疫仍是未知之數。
detail_en: The patient resides at Port Centre, Aberdeen, and is a part-time janitor at Bridal Tea House, Yau Ma Tei. She was responsible for cleaning numerous rooms at the hotel on June 30, including Room 503 where patient #11920 stayed between June 20 and 27. She undertook a test at a mobile specimen collection station on Arran Street, Yau Ma Tei after work, testing preliminarily positive, with CT value exceeding 30 denoting a low viral load. She was diagnosed positive on July 1 and her specimen contains the L452R mutation. She also works as a part-time janitor at Bluejay Residences, Ap Lei Chau and No. 2, 12A, South Bay Road, Repulse Bay, last attending work on June 27 and June 29 respectively. On June 26 she accompanied her children at tutorial sessions at Bayshore Apartments, Aberdeen Main Road, and played mahjong with friends at Kong Fu Court, Aberdeen Centre on June 27 and June 30. The Department of Health reported that the patient tested negative for both the virus and its antibodies, thus it cannot be concluded whether she was indeed infected.

detail_en: The patient, the husband of patient #11926, arrived in Hong Kong from Russia on June 29 and developed symptoms on July 1. His specimen contains the L452R mutation.

detail_en: The patient stays at Kerry Hotel, Hong Kong, Hung Hom upon arrival in Hong Kong from Korea, and tested positive on the 3rd day since arrival, having exhibited no symptoms. The patient received his first dose of BioNTech vaccine on April 8 in Hong Kong, but it was no ascertained why he did not receive the second dose.

detail_en: The patient studies abroad in the UK and is a close contact of patient #11944. He stays at Regal Airport Hotel, Chek Lap Kok upon arrival in Hong Kong and developed symptoms on July 3. His specimen contains the L452R mutation.

detail_en: The patient is a sailor arriving in Hong Kong from the Philippines by flight OZ721 on July 6, having exhibited no symptoms. The viral load of his specimen is too low to be determined whether it carries a mutation.

classification_zh: 輸入個案的密切接觸者
detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，與朋友同住於黃大仙金鳳街 1 至 3 號，在機場任職搬運工人，主要於停機坪工作，與機组人員及乘客沒有直接接觸及交流，最後上班日期為 7 月 10 日。6 月 24 日的檢測呈陰性，7 月 9 日因工作地點接受強制檢測，其樣本呈陽性，CT值達19，帶有 L452R 變種病毒。患者曾於 7 月 1 日接種首劑復必泰疫苗，潛伏期曾到訪多間食肆及海洋公園，亦曾到深水埗剪頭髮。患者於潛伏期間曾於一名由莫斯科抵港的確診機組人員（第 #11947 宗個案患者）工作的機艙逗留數小時。期間與該名確診機組人員並無直接接觸，數名回航莫斯科的機組人員亦一直逗留機艙內，估計患者可能從該俄羅斯抵港航班中其他沒有被診斷的機組人員感染。
detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, resides with friends at 1-3 Kam Fung Street, Wong Tai Sin, and works as a porter at the airport. He mainly works at the parking bays and has no direct contact or interaction with flight crews and passangers, last attending work on July 10. He tested negative during a mandatory testing on June 24, and tested positive for a mandatory testing at his workplace on July 9. His CT value is 19 and his specimen contains the L452R mutation. On July 1 he received the first dose of BioNTech vaccine, and he visited several restaurants and the Ocean Park throughout his incubation period, and had a haircut in Sham Shui Po. During his incubation period, the patient stayed at an aircraft cabin for several hours where a diagnosed flight crew member (patient #11947) arriving from Moscow had worked; they had no direct contact. As aeveral other flight crew members returning to Moscow also stayed in the cabin, the patient possibly contracted the virus from undiagnosed flight crew members from the said flight.

The CT value standing between 36 and 38 and the positive antibody test result denote that the infection took place at least 10 days ago. The viral load is too low to determine the presence of mutation. CHP postulate that the patient's case may be a 're-positive' case.
